INSERT INTO `articles` VALUES (1,'Como instalar o Node.JS no Windows 10','Como-instalar-o-Node.JS-no-Windows-10','<p id=\"e8f4\" class=\"gg gh dc bk gi b gj gk gl gm gn go gp gq gr gs gt cu\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\">Abra, em seu navegador, o link:</p>\r\n<p id=\"7594\" class=\"gg gh dc bk gi b gj gk gl gm gn go gp gq gr gs gt cu\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\"><a class=\" cimg-fluid at cg gu gv gw gx\" href=\"https://nodejs.org/en/download/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">https://nodejs.org/en/download/</a></p>\r\n<p id=\"b63f\" class=\"gg gh dc bk gi b gj gk gl gm gn go gp gq gr gs gt cu\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\">Escolha o instalador para a sua plataforma (Sistema Operacional) e arquitetura do processador (32-bits ou 64-bits). Caso n&atilde;o saiba qual o seu tipo de sistema, siga os passos do meu outro tutorial:&nbsp;<a class=\"at cg gu gv gw gx\" href=\"https://goo.gl/oa5r1d\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">aqui</a>.</p>\r\n<p class=\" img-fluid gg gh dc bk gi b gj gk gl gm gn go gp gq gr gs gt cu\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://miro.medium.com/max/906/1*NbZZAD5PvL6wDbwEWidvpw.gif\" alt=\"Download do Node.js\" width=\"906\" height=\"509\" /></p>\r\n<p id=\"e201\" class=\"gg gh dc bk gi b gj gk gl gm gn go gp gq gr gs gt cu\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\">Ao clicar no link do seu instalador, escolha a pasta para onde o download ser&aacute; feito (caso seu navegador j&aacute; n&atilde;o baixe para a pasta padr&atilde;o /downloads).</p>\r\n<p id=\"eee6\" class=\"gg gh dc bk gi b gj gk gl gm gn go gp gq gr gs gt cu\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\">Depois basta clicar duas vezes no arquivo baixado e seguir os passos dados na janela de instala&ccedil;&atilde;o. Por padr&atilde;o, voc&ecirc; n&atilde;o precisa alterar nada: apenas siga clicando em &ldquo;Next&rdquo;.</p>\r\n<p id=\"5a20\" class=\"gg gh dc bk gi b gj gk gl gm gn go gp gq gr gs gt cu\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\">Pronto, o Node est&aacute; instalado na sua m&aacute;quina. Para conferir a vers&atilde;o, abra uma janela de comandos (clique em &ldquo;iniciar&rdquo;, digite &ldquo;cmd&rdquo; e depois clique no item &ldquo;Prompt de Comando&rdquo;) e digite&nbsp;<strong class=\"gi hd\">node -v</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"gg gh dc bk gi b gj gk gl gm gn go gp gq gr gs gt cu\" style=\"text-align: center;\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\"><strong class=\"gi hd\"><img src=\"https://miro.medium.com/max/422/1*mAE9vo30PucMyfybnuuWmg.gif\" alt=\"Versao do node no CMD\" width=\"422\" height=\"289\" /></strong></p>\r\n<pre class=\"gg gh dc bk gi b gj gk gl gm gn go gp gq gr gs gt cu\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Vers&atilde;o do Node JS instalada no Windows</span></pre>\r\n<p class=\"gg gh dc bk gi b gj gk gl gm gn go gp gq gr gs gt cu\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\">&nbsp;</p>','2020-02-10 15:27:42','2020-02-28 11:54:09',1),(2,'PHP Tutorial','PHP-Tutorial','<p><strong>PHP</strong>&nbsp;&eacute; uma linguagem de programa&ccedil;&atilde;o bem vers&aacute;til e muito familiar a linguagem HTML. O c&oacute;digo&nbsp;<strong>PHP</strong>&nbsp;est&aacute; escrito entre as tags&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">&lt;?php ?&gt;</span>, como &eacute; mostrado na&nbsp;<strong>Listagem 1</strong>.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class=\"videoWrapper\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/fb6sEbF8U7U?rel=0&amp;controls=0\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"></iframe></div>\r\n<div class=\"lf-nota\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Relacionado:</strong>&nbsp;<a title=\"Introdu&ccedil;&atilde;o ao PHP\" href=\"https://www.devmedia.com.br/curso/introducao-ao-php/2171\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Introdu&ccedil;&atilde;o ao PHP</a></div>\r\n<div class=\"lf-nota\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"code-area\">\r\n<div class=\"pre_php code-sample\">\r\n<div><code class=\"code-sample\"></code>\r\n<div>\r\n<div id=\"highlighter_581314\" class=\"syntaxhighlighter  php\">\r\n<table style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"gutter\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\">1</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\">2</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\">3</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number4 index3 alt1\">4</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number5 index4 alt2\">5</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number6 index5 alt1\">6</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number7 index6 alt2\">7</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number8 index7 alt1\">8</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number9 index8 alt2\">9</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td class=\"code\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\"><code class=\"php plain\">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\"><code class=\"php plain\">&lt;html&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\"><code class=\"php spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"php plain\">&lt;body&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number4 index3 alt1\"><code class=\"php spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"php plain\">&lt;h1&gt;Estamos aprendendo PHP!&lt;/h1&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number5 index4 alt2\"><code class=\"php spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"php plain\">&lt;?php</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number6 index5 alt1\"><code class=\"php spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"php functions\">echo</code> <code class=\"php string\">\"Vamos prosseguir aprendendo PHP\"</code><code class=\"php plain\">; </code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number7 index6 alt2\"><code class=\"php spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"php plain\">?&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number8 index7 alt1\"><code class=\"php spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"php plain\">&lt;/body&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number9 index8 alt2\"><code class=\"php plain\">&lt;/html&gt;</code></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"code-caption\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Listagem 1</strong>. Exemplo de uso do&nbsp;<strong>PHP</strong>(index.php)</div>\r\n<div class=\"code-caption\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>O arquivo index foi salvo com a extens&atilde;o .php para mostrarmos ao nosso interpretador que h&aacute; um c&oacute;digo&nbsp;<strong>PHP</strong>&nbsp;a ser interpretado. Al&eacute;m disso, no exemplo usamos a fun&ccedil;&atilde;o&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">echo</span>&nbsp;para escrever na tela uma mensagem.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 id=\"comentar\">Como comentar o c&oacute;digo no PHP</h3>\r\n<p>Para comentarmos o nosso c&oacute;digo&nbsp;<strong>PHP</strong>&nbsp;usamos duas barras ou # para coment&aacute;rios de uma linha, e para coment&aacute;rios de m&uacute;ltiplas linhas usamos /* */, o mesmo usado no CSS. Observe alguns exemplos na&nbsp;<strong>Listagem 2</strong>.</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-area\">\r\n<div class=\"pre_php code-sample\">\r\n<div><code class=\"code-sample\"></code>\r\n<div>\r\n<div id=\"highlighter_17121\" class=\"syntaxhighlighter  php\">\r\n<table style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"gutter\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\">1</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\">2</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\">3</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number4 index3 alt1\">4</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number5 index4 alt2\">5</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number6 index5 alt1\">6</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number7 index6 alt2\">7</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number8 index7 alt1\">8</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number9 index8 alt2\">9</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number10 index9 alt1\">10</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number11 index10 alt2\">11</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td class=\"code\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\"><code class=\"php plain\">&lt;?php</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\"><code class=\"php spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"php functions\">echo</code> <code class=\"php string\">\"Oi, Eu serei visto na sua tela\"</code><code class=\"php plain\">;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\"><code class=\"php spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"php comments\">// Eu n&atilde;o! Sou apenas um coment&aacute;rio.</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number4 index3 alt1\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number5 index4 alt2\"><code class=\"php spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"php functions\">echo</code> <code class=\"php string\">\"Oi, Eu tamb&eacute;m serei visto por voc&ecirc;\"</code><code class=\"php plain\">;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number6 index5 alt1\"><code class=\"php spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"php plain\"># J&aacute; eu n&atilde;o serei!</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number7 index6 alt2\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number8 index7 alt1\"><code class=\"php spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"php functions\">echo</code> <code class=\"php string\">\"E eu aqui novamente na sua tela, rs\"</code><code class=\"php plain\">;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number9 index8 alt2\"><code class=\"php spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"php comments\">/* Eu n&atilde;o aparecerei na sua tela novamente</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number10 index9 alt1\"><code class=\"php spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"php comments\">pois sou um coment&aacute;rio */</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number11 index10 alt2\"><code class=\"php plain\">?&gt;</code></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"code-caption\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Listagem 2</strong>. Exemplo de coment&aacute;rios no&nbsp;<strong>PHP&nbsp;</strong>utilizando //, # ou /**/</div>\r\n<div class=\"code-caption\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3 id=\"variaveis\">Vari&aacute;veis no PHP</h3>\r\n<p>Para criarmos uma vari&aacute;vel basta utilizar o sinal de cifr&atilde;o. Uma vari&aacute;vel pode armazenar textos e n&uacute;meros. Al&eacute;m disso, a linguagem PHP &eacute; case sensitive, ent&atilde;o A &eacute; diferente de a. Observe um exemplo de uso de vari&aacute;veis na&nbsp;<strong>Listagem 3</strong>.</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-area\">\r\n<div class=\"pre_php code-sample\">\r\n<div><code class=\"code-sample\"></code>\r\n<div>\r\n<div id=\"highlighter_398179\" class=\"syntaxhighlighter  php\">\r\n<table style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"gutter\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\">1</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\">2</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\">3</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number4 index3 alt1\">4</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number5 index4 alt2\">5</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number6 index5 alt1\">6</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number7 index6 alt2\">7</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number8 index7 alt1\">8</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td class=\"code\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\"><code class=\"php plain\">&lt;?php</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\"><code class=\"php spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"php variable\">$name</code> <code class=\"php plain\">= </code><code class=\"php string\">\"Guilherme\"</code><code class=\"php plain\">;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\"><code class=\"php spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"php variable\">$age</code> <code class=\"php plain\">= 20;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number4 index3 alt1\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number5 index4 alt2\"><code class=\"php spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"php functions\">echo</code> <code class=\"php variable\">$name</code><code class=\"php plain\">; </code><code class=\"php comments\">// Guilherme</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number6 index5 alt1\"><code class=\"php spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"php functions\">echo</code> <code class=\"php string\">\"&lt;/br&gt;\"</code><code class=\"php plain\">;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number7 index6 alt2\"><code class=\"php spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"php functions\">echo</code> <code class=\"php variable\">$age</code><code class=\"php plain\">; </code><code class=\"php comments\">// 20</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number8 index7 alt1\"><code class=\"php plain\">?&gt;</code></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"code-caption\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Listagem 3</strong>. Exemplo de Vari&aacute;veis</div>\r\n<div class=\"code-caption\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>No exemplo criamos uma vari&aacute;vel&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">$name</span>&nbsp;e declaramos a ela uma string, sendo assim precisamos coloc&aacute;-la entre aspas. J&aacute; a outra vari&aacute;vel&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">$age</span>&nbsp;&eacute; declarada como inteiro, ent&atilde;o n&atilde;o &eacute; necess&aacute;rio o uso de aspas. Ao usarmos o comando&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">echo</span>&nbsp;nas vari&aacute;veis, o resultado impresso &eacute; o conte&uacute;do dessa vari&aacute;vel.</p>\r\n<p>Para a nomea&ccedil;&atilde;o de vari&aacute;veis, as dicas a seguir s&atilde;o necess&aacute;rias:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>N&atilde;o inicie o nome de uma vari&aacute;vel com n&uacute;meros;</li>\r\n<li>N&atilde;o utilize espa&ccedil;os em brancos;</li>\r\n<li>N&atilde;o utilize caracteres especiais, somente underline;</li>\r\n<li>Crie vari&aacute;veis com nomes que ajudar&atilde;o a identificar melhor a mesma;</li>\r\n<li>Evite utilizar letras mai&uacute;sculas.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Falaremos agora sobre alguns dos tipos de vari&aacute;veis que existem no&nbsp;<strong>PHP</strong>:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Booleanos</strong>: Este &eacute; o tipo mais simples, pois s&oacute; pode expressar apenas dois valores:&nbsp;<strong>TRUE (1)</strong>&nbsp;ou&nbsp;<strong>FALSE (0, null ou uma string vazia);</strong></li>\r\n<li><strong>Integer</strong>: &eacute; um n&uacute;mero inteiro, podendo ser negativo ou positivo;</li>\r\n<li><strong>Float</strong>: tamb&eacute;m chamado de double ou n&uacute;meros reais representados com um ponto para separar os d&iacute;gitos do valor inteiro dos d&iacute;gitos do valor das casas decimais.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Strings</strong>: &eacute; uma palavra ou frase entre aspas simples ou duplas, assim como tamb&eacute;m pode ser bin&aacute;rio, como o conte&uacute;do de um arquivo MP3 ou JPG. Veja os exemplos na&nbsp;<strong>Listagem 4.</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div class=\"code-area\">\r\n<div class=\"pre_php code-sample\">\r\n<div><code class=\"code-sample\"></code>\r\n<div>\r\n<div id=\"highlighter_454760\" class=\"syntaxhighlighter  php\">\r\n<table style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"gutter\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\">1</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\">2</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\">3</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number4 index3 alt1\">4</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number5 index4 alt2\">5</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td class=\"code\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\"><code class=\"php plain\">&lt;?php</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\"><code class=\"php spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"php variable\">$a</code> <code class=\"php plain\">= </code><code class=\"php string\">\"mundo!\"</code><code class=\"php plain\">;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\"><code class=\"php spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"php functions\">echo</code> <code class=\"php string\">\"Ol&aacute;, $a\"</code><code class=\"php plain\">; </code><code class=\"php comments\">// Ol&aacute;, mundo!</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number4 index3 alt1\"><code class=\"php spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"php functions\">echo</code> <code class=\"php string\">\'Ol&aacute;, $a\'</code><code class=\"php plain\">; </code><code class=\"php comments\">// Ol&aacute;, $a</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number5 index4 alt2\"><code class=\"php plain\">?&gt;</code></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"code-caption\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Listagem 4</strong>. Exemplos de String</div>\r\n<div class=\"code-caption\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>Note que quando declaramos no&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">echo \"Ol&aacute;, $a\";</span>, o PHP interpretou o conte&uacute;do da vari&aacute;vel&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">$a</span>, pois est&aacute; entre aspas duplas. E quando usamos a mesma forma, s&oacute; que entre aspas simples&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">echo \'Ol&aacute;, $a\';</span>, n&atilde;o temos o mesmo resultado. Ent&atilde;o quando queremos que o PHP interprete o valor de nossa vari&aacute;vel dentro de uma string &eacute; necess&aacute;rio o uso de aspas duplas.</p>\r\n<p>Al&eacute;m disso, podemos usar um ponto para concatenar strings, assim como o sinal + para o JavaScript, como mostra o c&oacute;digo da&nbsp;<strong>Listagem 5</strong>.</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-area\">\r\n<div class=\"pre_php code-sample\">\r\n<div><code class=\"code-sample\"></code>\r\n<div>\r\n<div id=\"highlighter_115059\" class=\"syntaxhighlighter  php\">\r\n<table style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"gutter\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\">1</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\">2</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\">3</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number4 index3 alt1\">4</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td class=\"code\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\"><code class=\"php plain\">&lt;?php</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\"><code class=\"php spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"php functions\">echo</code> <code class=\"php string\">\"Ol&aacute;,\"</code> <code class=\"php plain\">. </code><code class=\"php string\">\" mundo!\"</code><code class=\"php plain\">;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\"><code class=\"php spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"php comments\">//Ol&aacute;, mundo!</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number4 index3 alt1\"><code class=\"php plain\">?&gt;</code></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"code-caption\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Listagem 5</strong>. Exemplo concatena&ccedil;&atilde;o de String</div>\r\n<div class=\"code-caption\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3 id=\"constantes\">Constantes no PHP</h3>\r\n<p>O valor de uma constante jamais poder&aacute; ser alterado enquanto estiver sendo executada e para defini-la utilizamos a fun&ccedil;&atilde;o&nbsp;<em>define()</em>&nbsp;ou&nbsp;<em>const</em>, como mostra a&nbsp;<strong>Listagem 6</strong>.</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-area\">\r\n<div class=\"pre_php code-sample\">\r\n<div><code class=\"code-sample\"></code>\r\n<div>\r\n<div id=\"highlighter_598602\" class=\"syntaxhighlighter  php\">\r\n<table style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"gutter\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\">1</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\">2</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\">3</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number4 index3 alt1\">4</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number5 index4 alt2\">5</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number6 index5 alt1\">6</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number7 index6 alt2\">7</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number8 index7 alt1\">8</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number9 index8 alt2\">9</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td class=\"code\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\"><code class=\"php plain\">&lt;?php</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\"><code class=\"php spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"php plain\">define(</code><code class=\"php string\">\"PHP\"</code><code class=\"php plain\">, </code><code class=\"php string\">\"Linguagem Open - Source\"</code><code class=\"php plain\">);</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number4 index3 alt1\"><code class=\"php spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"php keyword\">const</code> <code class=\"php plain\">HTML = </code><code class=\"php string\">\"Linguagem de marca&ccedil;&atilde;o\"</code><code class=\"php plain\">;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number5 index4 alt2\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number6 index5 alt1\"><code class=\"php spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"php functions\">echo</code> <code class=\"php plain\">PHP; </code><code class=\"php comments\">// Linguagem Open - Source</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number7 index6 alt2\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number8 index7 alt1\"><code class=\"php spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"php functions\">echo</code> <code class=\"php plain\">HTML; </code><code class=\"php comments\">// Linguagem de marca&ccedil;&atilde;o</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number9 index8 alt2\"><code class=\"php plain\">?&gt;</code></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"code-caption\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Listagem 6</strong>. Exemplo de Constantes</div>\r\n<div class=\"code-caption\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>Utilizando a fun&ccedil;&atilde;o&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">define()</span>&nbsp;ou a palavra reservada&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">const</span>&nbsp;definimos que as constantes com os nomes de PHP e HTML respectivamente, com o valor: Linguagem Open &ndash; Source e Linguagem de marca&ccedil;&atilde;o.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 id=\"arrays\">Arrays no PHP</h3>\r\n<p>Um&nbsp;<em>array</em>&nbsp;que mant&eacute;m uma s&eacute;rie de elementos que podem ter diferentes tipos, como mostra a&nbsp;<strong>Listagem 7</strong>.</p>\r\n<div class=\"lf-nota\">Saiba mais sobre&nbsp;<a title=\"array php\" href=\"http://www.devmedia.com.br/php-declaracao-e-atribuicao-de-arrays-em-php/38621\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Arrays no PHP</a></div>\r\n<div class=\"code-area\">\r\n<div class=\"pre_php code-sample\">\r\n<div><code class=\"code-sample\"></code>\r\n<div>\r\n<div id=\"highlighter_92177\" class=\"syntaxhighlighter  php\">\r\n<table style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"gutter\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\">1</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\">2</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\">3</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number4 index3 alt1\">4</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number5 index4 alt2\">5</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number6 index5 alt1\">6</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number7 index6 alt2\">7</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number8 index7 alt1\">8</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td class=\"code\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\"><code class=\"php plain\">&lt;?php</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\"><code class=\"php spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"php variable\">$php</code> <code class=\"php plain\">= </code><code class=\"php keyword\">array</code><code class=\"php plain\">(</code><code class=\"php string\">\"Zend\"</code> <code class=\"php plain\">=&gt; </code><code class=\"php string\">\"CERTIFICA&Ccedil;&Atilde;O\"</code><code class=\"php plain\">, 6 =&gt; false);</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\"><code class=\"php spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"php functions\">echo</code> <code class=\"php variable\">$php</code><code class=\"php plain\">[</code><code class=\"php string\">\"Zend\"</code><code class=\"php plain\">]; </code><code class=\"php comments\">// CERTIFICA&Ccedil;&Atilde;O</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number4 index3 alt1\"><code class=\"php spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"php functions\">echo</code> <code class=\"php variable\">$php</code><code class=\"php plain\">[6]; </code><code class=\"php comments\">// 0</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number5 index4 alt2\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number6 index5 alt1\"><code class=\"php spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"php comments\">// Zend &eacute; nossa chave e CERTIFICA&Ccedil;&Atilde;O nosso valor</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number7 index6 alt2\"><code class=\"php spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"php comments\">// 6 &eacute; nossa chave e false(0) &eacute; nosso valor</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number8 index7 alt1\"><code class=\"php plain\">?&gt;</code></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"code-caption\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Listagem 7</strong>. Exemplo de arrays</div>\r\n<div class=\"code-caption\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>Note que nossa primeira chave se chama Zend, e a outra chama-se 6, mas quanto a nomea&ccedil;&atilde;o de chaves de array pode ser tanto string ou um integer. Para o valor pode ser qualquer coisa.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 id=\"conversao\">Convers&atilde;o de tipos</h3>\r\n<p>Os tipos de&nbsp;<strong><a title=\"PHP: Declara&ccedil;&atilde;o e atribui&ccedil;&atilde;o de vari&aacute;veis\" href=\"http://www.devmedia.com.br/php-declaracao-e-atribuicao-de-variaveis/38220\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">vari&aacute;veis no PHP</a></strong>&nbsp;s&atilde;o din&acirc;micos. Para for&ccedil;armos os tipos de nossas vari&aacute;veis utilizamos uma t&eacute;cnica conhecida como type casting, ou simplesmente troca de tipos. Veja na&nbsp;<strong>Listagem 8</strong>&nbsp;alguns exemplos.</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-area\">\r\n<div class=\"pre_php code-sample\">\r\n<div><code class=\"code-sample\"></code>\r\n<div>\r\n<div id=\"highlighter_239477\" class=\"syntaxhighlighter  php\">\r\n<table style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"gutter\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\">1</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\">2</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\">3</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number4 index3 alt1\">4</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number5 index4 alt2\">5</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number6 index5 alt1\">6</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number7 index6 alt2\">7</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number8 index7 alt1\">8</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number9 index8 alt2\">9</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td class=\"code\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\"><code class=\"php plain\">&lt;?php</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\"><code class=\"php spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"php variable\">$var</code> <code class=\"php plain\">= 100;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\"><code class=\"php spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"php variable\">$type_casting</code> <code class=\"php plain\">= (bool) </code><code class=\"php variable\">$var</code><code class=\"php plain\">; </code><code class=\"php comments\">// torna &ndash; se booleano</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number4 index3 alt1\"><code class=\"php spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"php variable\">$type_casting</code> <code class=\"php plain\">= (int) </code><code class=\"php variable\">$var</code><code class=\"php plain\">; </code><code class=\"php comments\">// torna &ndash; se inteiro</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number5 index4 alt2\"><code class=\"php spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"php variable\">$type_casting</code> <code class=\"php plain\">= (float) </code><code class=\"php variable\">$var</code><code class=\"php plain\">; </code><code class=\"php comments\">// torna &ndash; se float</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number6 index5 alt1\"><code class=\"php spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"php variable\">$type_casting</code> <code class=\"php plain\">= (string) </code><code class=\"php variable\">$var</code><code class=\"php plain\">; </code><code class=\"php comments\">// torna &ndash; se string</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number7 index6 alt2\"><code class=\"php spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"php variable\">$type_casting</code> <code class=\"php plain\">= (</code><code class=\"php keyword\">array</code><code class=\"php plain\">) </code><code class=\"php variable\">$var</code><code class=\"php plain\">; </code><code class=\"php comments\">// torna &ndash; se array</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number8 index7 alt1\"><code class=\"php spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"php functions\">echo</code> <code class=\"php variable\">$type_casting</code> <code class=\"php plain\">= (bool)</code><code class=\"php variable\">$var</code><code class=\"php plain\">; </code><code class=\"php comments\">// 1</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number9 index8 alt2\"><code class=\"php plain\">?&gt;</code></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"code-caption\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Listagem 8</strong>. Exemplo de convers&atilde;o de tipos</div>\r\n<div class=\"code-caption\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>Veja que transformamos o valor da&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">$var</span>, que antes era um inteiro, para um valor booleano.</p>\r\n<p>Vamos conhecer agora&nbsp;<strong>operadores</strong>, que permitem que n&oacute;s manipulemos o conte&uacute;do de uma ou mais vari&aacute;veis.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 id=\"aritmeticos\">Operadores Aritm&eacute;ticos no PHP</h3>\r\n<p>Podemos utilizar operadores matem&aacute;ticos para efetuar c&aacute;lculos com os valores de vari&aacute;veis, como mostra a&nbsp;<strong>Listagem 9</strong>.</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-area\">\r\n<div class=\"pre_php code-sample\">\r\n<div><code class=\"code-sample\"></code>\r\n<div>\r\n<div id=\"highlighter_87647\" class=\"syntaxhighlighter  php\">\r\n<table style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"gutter\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\">1</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\">2</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\">3</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number4 index3 alt1\">4</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number5 index4 alt2\">5</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number6 index5 alt1\">6</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number7 index6 alt2\">7</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td class=\"code\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\"><code class=\"php plain\">&lt;?php</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\"><code class=\"php spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"php variable\">$a</code> <code class=\"php plain\">= 3;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\"><code class=\"php spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"php variable\">$b</code> <code class=\"php plain\">= 3;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number4 index3 alt1\"><code class=\"php spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"php variable\">$c</code> <code class=\"php plain\">= </code><code class=\"php variable\">$a</code> <code class=\"php plain\">* </code><code class=\"php variable\">$b</code><code class=\"php plain\">; </code><code class=\"php comments\">// resultado &eacute; 9</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number5 index4 alt2\"><code class=\"php spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"php variable\">$d</code> <code class=\"php plain\">= </code><code class=\"php variable\">$a</code> <code class=\"php plain\">+ </code><code class=\"php variable\">$b</code><code class=\"php plain\">; </code><code class=\"php comments\">// resultado &eacute; 6</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number6 index5 alt1\"><code class=\"php spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"php variable\">$e</code> <code class=\"php plain\">= </code><code class=\"php variable\">$c</code> <code class=\"php plain\">- </code><code class=\"php variable\">$d</code><code class=\"php plain\">; </code><code class=\"php comments\">// resultado &eacute; 3</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number7 index6 alt2\"><code class=\"php plain\">?&gt;</code></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"code-caption\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Listagem 9</strong>. Exemplo de operadores aritm&eacute;ticos</div>\r\n<div class=\"code-caption\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>Criamos as vari&aacute;veis&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">$a</span>&nbsp;e&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">$b</span>&nbsp;e a partir delas conseguimos fazer v&aacute;rios c&aacute;lculos matem&aacute;ticos.</p>\r\n<p>Os operadores matem&aacute;ticos dispon&iacute;veis em PHP s&atilde;o:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Adi&ccedil;&atilde;o: +</li>\r\n<li>Subtra&ccedil;&atilde;o: -</li>\r\n<li>Multiplica&ccedil;&atilde;o: *</li>\r\n<li>Divis&atilde;o: /</li>\r\n<li>M&oacute;dulo: %</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Lembrando que n&atilde;o precisamos especificar os tipos de vari&aacute;veis no PHP, como nos exemplos a seguir:</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-area\">\r\n<div class=\"pre_php code-sample\">\r\n<div><code class=\"code-sample\"></code>\r\n<div>\r\n<div id=\"highlighter_361248\" class=\"syntaxhighlighter  php\">\r\n<table style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"gutter\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\">1</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\">2</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\">3</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number4 index3 alt1\">4</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number5 index4 alt2\">5</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td class=\"code\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\"><code class=\"php plain\">&lt;?php</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\"><code class=\"php spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"php variable\">$a</code> <code class=\"php plain\">= </code><code class=\"php string\">\"5\"</code><code class=\"php plain\">; </code><code class=\"php comments\">// string</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\"><code class=\"php spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"php functions\">echo</code> <code class=\"php variable\">$a</code> <code class=\"php plain\">+ 2; </code><code class=\"php comments\">// 7, integer</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number4 index3 alt1\"><code class=\"php spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"php functions\">echo</code> <code class=\"php variable\">$a</code> <code class=\"php plain\">+ </code><code class=\"php string\">\'5 carros\'</code><code class=\"php plain\">; </code><code class=\"php comments\">// 10, integer</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number5 index4 alt2\"><code class=\"php plain\">?&gt;</code></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Note que&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">$a</span>&nbsp;&eacute; uma string e quando demos um&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">echo</span>&nbsp;nela somando com 2, que &eacute; um inteiro, o resultado retornado foi 7. Isso demonstra que nossos tipos de vari&aacute;veis em PHP s&atilde;o sempre din&acirc;micos. E na linha 4 o PHP reconhece dentro das aspas simples um numeral e com isso executa a opera&ccedil;&atilde;o matem&aacute;tica e exibir&aacute; o resultado 10 do tipo inteiro mas n&atilde;o exibindo a palavra \"carros\".</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 id=\"atribuicao\">Operadores de Atribui&ccedil;&atilde;o no PHP</h3>\r\n<p>Utilizamos os operadores de atribui&ccedil;&atilde;o para definir vari&aacute;veis e seus valores, al&eacute;m de us&aacute;-los juntamente com os operadores matem&aacute;ticos, como mostra o exemplo da&nbsp;<strong>Listagem 10</strong>.</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-area\">\r\n<div class=\"pre_php code-sample\">\r\n<div><code class=\"code-sample\"></code>\r\n<div>\r\n<div id=\"highlighter_909572\" class=\"syntaxhighlighter  php\">\r\n<table style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"gutter\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\">1</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\">2</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\">3</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number4 index3 alt1\">4</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number5 index4 alt2\">5</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td class=\"code\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\"><code class=\"php plain\">&lt;?php</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\"><code class=\"php spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"php variable\">$a</code> <code class=\"php plain\">= 1; </code><code class=\"php comments\">// A vari&aacute;vel $a &eacute; igual a 1</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\"><code class=\"php spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"php variable\">$a</code> <code class=\"php plain\">+= 2; </code><code class=\"php comments\">// Somamos 2 ao valor da $a;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number4 index3 alt1\"><code class=\"php spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"php functions\">echo</code> <code class=\"php variable\">$a</code><code class=\"php plain\">;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number5 index4 alt2\"><code class=\"php plain\">?&gt;</code></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"code-caption\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Listagem 10</strong>. Exemplo de Operadores de Atribui&ccedil;&atilde;o com Operadores Matem&aacute;ticos</div>\r\n<div class=\"code-caption\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>O resultado acima &eacute; 3, pois somamos 2 ao valor da&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">$a</span>, que &eacute; 1. Na&nbsp;<strong>Listagem 11</strong>&nbsp;temos mais exemplos.</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-area\">\r\n<div class=\"pre_php code-sample\">\r\n<div><code class=\"code-sample\"></code>\r\n<div>\r\n<div id=\"highlighter_140752\" class=\"syntaxhighlighter  php\">\r\n<table style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"gutter\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\">1</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\">2</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\">3</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number4 index3 alt1\">4</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number5 index4 alt2\">5</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td class=\"code\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\"><code class=\"php plain\">&lt;?php</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\"><code class=\"php spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"php variable\">$a</code> <code class=\"php plain\">-= 2; </code><code class=\"php comments\">// Subtra&iacute;mos 2 ao valor da vari&aacute;vel $a;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\"><code class=\"php spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"php variable\">$a</code> <code class=\"php plain\">*= 2; </code><code class=\"php comments\">// Multiplicamos o valor da vari&aacute;vel $a por 2;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number4 index3 alt1\"><code class=\"php spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"php variable\">$a</code> <code class=\"php plain\">/= 2; </code><code class=\"php comments\">// Dividimos o valor da vari&aacute;vel $a por 2.</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number5 index4 alt2\"><code class=\"php plain\">?&gt;</code></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"code-caption\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Listagem 11</strong>. Exemplo de Operadores de Atribui&ccedil;&atilde;o com Operadores Matem&aacute;ticos</div>\r\n<div class=\"code-caption\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>A sintaxe desses operadores &eacute; a mesma do exemplo da soma, pois basta dar um echo depois de ter declarado a vari&aacute;vel com seu respectivo operador.</p>\r\n<p>Podemos tamb&eacute;m incrementar ou decrementar vari&aacute;veis utilizando os operadores de incrementa&ccedil;&atilde;o, herdados da linguagem C, como nos exemplos da&nbsp;<strong>Listagem 12</strong>.</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-area\">\r\n<div class=\"pre_php code-sample\">\r\n<div><code class=\"code-sample\"></code>\r\n<div>\r\n<div id=\"highlighter_793455\" class=\"syntaxhighlighter  php\">\r\n<table style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"gutter\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\">1</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\">2</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\">3</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number4 index3 alt1\">4</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number5 index4 alt2\">5</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number6 index5 alt1\">6</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number7 index6 alt2\">7</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td class=\"code\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\"><code class=\"php plain\">&lt;?php</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\"><code class=\"php spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"php variable\">$a</code> <code class=\"php plain\">= 1;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\"><code class=\"php spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"php functions\">echo</code> <code class=\"php plain\">++</code><code class=\"php variable\">$a</code><code class=\"php plain\">; </code><code class=\"php comments\">// Incrementamos 1 e retornamos o valor</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number4 index3 alt1\"><code class=\"php spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"php functions\">echo</code> <code class=\"php variable\">$a</code><code class=\"php plain\">++; </code><code class=\"php comments\">// Retornamos o valor e incrementamos 1</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number5 index4 alt2\"><code class=\"php spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"php functions\">echo</code> <code class=\"php plain\">--</code><code class=\"php variable\">$a</code><code class=\"php plain\">; </code><code class=\"php comments\">// Decrementamos 1 e retornamos o valor</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number6 index5 alt1\"><code class=\"php spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"php functions\">echo</code> <code class=\"php variable\">$a</code><code class=\"php plain\">--; </code><code class=\"php comments\">// Retornamos o valor e decrementamos 1</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number7 index6 alt2\"><code class=\"php plain\">?&gt;</code></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"code-caption\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Listagem 12</strong>. Exemplo de Operadores de Atribui&ccedil;&atilde;o - Incremento e decremento</div>\r\n<div class=\"code-caption\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3 id=\"relacionais\">Operadores Relacionais</h3>\r\n<p>Esses s&atilde;o usados para comparar valores ou express&otilde;es, retornando um valor booleano (true ou false):</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Igual: ==</li>\r\n<li>Id&ecirc;ntico: ===</li>\r\n<li>Diferente: != ou &lt;&gt;</li>\r\n<li>Menor que: &lt;</li>\r\n<li>Maior que: &gt;</li>\r\n<li>Menor ou igual: &lt;=</li>\r\n<li>Maior ou igual: &gt;=</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&Eacute; importante lembrar que == n&atilde;o checa o tipo da vari&aacute;vel, apenas seu valor. J&aacute; o&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">===</span>&nbsp;checa tanto o valor da vari&aacute;vel quanto o seu tipo.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 id=\"logicos\">Operadores L&oacute;gicos</h3>\r\n<p>Existem tamb&eacute;m os operadores l&oacute;gicos para a cria&ccedil;&atilde;o de testes condicionais:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>$a and $b: enquanto A e B forem verdadeiros;</li>\r\n<li>$a or $b: enquanto A ou B forem verdadeiros;</li>\r\n<li>$a xor $b: enquanto A ou B forem verdadeiros, mas n&atilde;o os dois;</li>\r\n<li>!$a: verdadeiro se A for falso;</li>\r\n<li>$a &amp;&amp; $b: enquanto A e B forem verdadeiros;</li>\r\n<li>$a || $b: enquanto A ou B forem verdadeiros.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3 id=\"ifelse\">Estrutura de Decis&atilde;o if/else</h3>\r\n<p>A condi&ccedil;&atilde;o &eacute; avaliada para que, caso algo seja verdadeiro, fa&ccedil;a isto, sen&atilde;o, fa&ccedil;a aquilo, como mostra a&nbsp;<strong>Listagem 13</strong>.</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-area\">\r\n<div class=\"pre_php code-sample\">\r\n<div><code class=\"code-sample\"></code>\r\n<div>\r\n<div id=\"highlighter_428034\" class=\"syntaxhighlighter  php\">\r\n<table style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"gutter\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\">1</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\">2</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\">3</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number4 index3 alt1\">4</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number5 index4 alt2\">5</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number6 index5 alt1\">6</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number7 index6 alt2\">7</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number8 index7 alt1\">8</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number9 index8 alt2\">9</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td class=\"code\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\"><code class=\"php plain\">&lt;?php</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\"><code class=\"php spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"php variable\">$idade</code> <code class=\"php plain\">= 17;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\"><code class=\"php spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</code>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number4 index3 alt1\"><code class=\"php spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"php keyword\">if</code><code class=\"php plain\">(</code><code class=\"php variable\">$idade</code> <code class=\"php plain\">&lt; 18) {</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number5 index4 alt2\"><code class=\"php spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"php functions\">echo</code> <code class=\"php string\">\'Voc&ecirc; n&atilde;o pode entrar aqui!\'</code><code class=\"php plain\">;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number6 index5 alt1\"><code class=\"php spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"php plain\">} </code><code class=\"php keyword\">else</code> <code class=\"php plain\">{</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number7 index6 alt2\"><code class=\"php spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"php functions\">echo</code> <code class=\"php string\">\'Seja bem &ndash; vindo\'</code><code class=\"php plain\">;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number8 index7 alt1\"><code class=\"php spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"php plain\">}</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number9 index8 alt2\"><code class=\"php plain\">?&gt;</code></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"code-caption\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Listagem 13</strong>. Exemplo do uso das estruturas de decis&atilde;o&nbsp;<strong>if/else</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"code-caption\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Na linha 1 criamos a vari&aacute;vel&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">$idade</span>&nbsp;que guarda um inteiro.</li>\r\n<li>Na linha 4 utilizamos&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">IF</span>&nbsp;para verificar se&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">$idade</span>&nbsp;&eacute; menor que 18, e caso seja ser&aacute; impresso: \"Voc&ecirc; n&atilde;o pode entra aqui!\"</li>\r\n<li>Na linha 6 criamos um&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">ELSE,</span>&nbsp;que &eacute; o contr&aacute;rio da primeira condi&ccedil;&atilde;o.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Podemos tamb&eacute;m utilizar os operadores l&oacute;gicos junto dos operadores relacionais, como mostra a&nbsp;<strong>Listagem 14</strong>.</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-area\">\r\n<div class=\"pre_php code-sample\">\r\n<div><code class=\"code-sample\"></code>\r\n<div>\r\n<div id=\"highlighter_428657\" class=\"syntaxhighlighter  php\">\r\n<table style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"gutter\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\">1</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\">2</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\">3</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number4 index3 alt1\">4</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number5 index4 alt2\">5</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number6 index5 alt1\">6</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number7 index6 alt2\">7</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number8 index7 alt1\">8</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td class=\"code\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\"><code class=\"php plain\">&lt;?php</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\"><code class=\"php variable\">$idade</code> <code class=\"php plain\">= 21;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\"><code class=\"php variable\">$identidade</code> <code class=\"php plain\">= true;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number4 index3 alt1\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number5 index4 alt2\"><code class=\"php keyword\">if</code><code class=\"php plain\">(</code><code class=\"php variable\">$idade</code> <code class=\"php plain\">&gt; 18 &amp;&amp; </code><code class=\"php variable\">$identidade</code> <code class=\"php plain\">== true) {</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number6 index5 alt1\"><code class=\"php spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"php functions\">echo</code> <code class=\"php string\">\'Seja bem-vindo!\'</code><code class=\"php plain\">;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number7 index6 alt2\"><code class=\"php plain\">}</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number8 index7 alt1\"><code class=\"php plain\">?&gt;</code></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"code-caption\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Listagem 14</strong>. Exemplo do uso de Operadores l&oacute;gicos com Operadores relacionais</div>\r\n</div>','2020-02-10 16:28:20','2020-02-24 16:52:04',4),(3,'Como instalar o React no Windows','Como-instalar-o-React-no-Windows','<section class=\"action-menu menu-action-top menu-hidden\">\r\n<p><span class=\"titulo_box_lead2\">Por que eu devo ler este artigo: </span><strong>React &eacute; a ferramenta de desenvolvimento front-end que mais cresce por ano em n&uacute;mero de usu&aacute;rios segundo o Stack Overflow</strong>. Neste artigo iremos aprender como criar a nossa primeira Aplica&ccedil;&atilde;o de P&aacute;gina &Uacute;nica (SPA) em React utilizando a ferramenta create-react-app do Facebook</p>\r\n</section>\r\n<section class=\"page-content main-content video-conteudo-area top-content\">\r\n<section class=\"page-content-wrapper\">\r\n<div class=\"breadcrumb\"><a title=\"Artigos\" href=\"http://www.devmedia.com.br/artigos/\">Artigos </a></div>\r\n<div class=\"breadcrumb\"><a title=\"Artigos de JavaScript\" href=\"https://www.devmedia.com.br/artigos/javascript\">JavaScript</a><span class=\"bread-artigo\">&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n<h3>Configurando o Ambiente</h3>\r\n<p><strong>React &eacute; uma biblioteca/framework JavaScript</strong>&nbsp;para criar aplica&ccedil;&otilde;es que rodam no navegador, por&eacute;m os pacotes que iremos utilizar durante o desenvolvimento ser&atilde;o gerenciados pelo Node Package Manager (NPM), inclusive o pr&oacute;prio React.</p>\r\n<p>Come&ccedil;aremos ent&atilde;o indo at&eacute; o site oficial do&nbsp;<a title=\"Site do Node.js\" href=\"https://nodejs.org/en/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Node.js</a>&nbsp;e iremos instalar sua vers&atilde;o LTS, como ilustra a&nbsp;<strong>Figura 1</strong>.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<figure class=\"lazy-img\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"imagem_artigo loaded\" style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://arquivo.devmedia.com.br/artigos/criando_projeto_react_40329/site_node.png\" alt=\"Site do Node.js\" width=\"738\" height=\"610\" />\r\n<figcaption><strong>Figura 1</strong>. Site do Node.js<br /><br /></figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<p>Quando&nbsp;<strong>instalamos o Node.js o NPM</strong>&nbsp;tamb&eacute;m &eacute; instalado no computador como parte do mesmo pacote, para utiliz&aacute;-lo basta abrir a ferramenta de linha de comando do seu sistema operacional, por exemplo o cmd do Windows ou o terminal do Linux, e digitar npm, uma lista com os comandos ser&aacute; exibida, como ilustra a&nbsp;<strong>Listagem 1</strong>.</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-area\">\r\n<div class=\"pre_shell code-sample\">\r\n<div><code class=\"code-sample\"></code>\r\n<div>\r\n<div id=\"highlighter_844433\" class=\"syntaxhighlighter  powershell\">\r\n<table style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"gutter\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\">1</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\">2</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\">3</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number4 index3 alt1\">4</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number5 index4 alt2\">5</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number6 index5 alt1\">6</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number7 index6 alt2\">7</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number8 index7 alt1\">8</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number9 index8 alt2\">9</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number10 index9 alt1\">10</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number11 index10 alt2\">11</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number12 index11 alt1\">12</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number13 index12 alt2\">13</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number14 index13 alt1\">14</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number15 index14 alt2\">15</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number16 index15 alt1\">16</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number17 index16 alt2\">17</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number18 index17 alt1\">18</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number19 index18 alt2\">19</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number20 index19 alt1\">20</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number21 index20 alt2\">21</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number22 index21 alt1\">22</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number23 index22 alt2\">23</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number24 index23 alt1\">24</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number25 index24 alt2\">25</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td class=\"code\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\"><code class=\"powershell plain\">C:\\Users\\Editorial&gt;npm</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\"><code class=\"powershell plain\">Usage: npm &lt;command&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number4 index3 alt1\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number5 index4 alt2\"><code class=\"powershell keyword\">where</code> <code class=\"powershell plain\">&lt;command&gt; is one of:</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number6 index5 alt1\"><code class=\"powershell spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"powershell plain\">access, adduser, audit, bin, bugs, c, cache, ci, cit,</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number7 index6 alt2\"><code class=\"powershell spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"powershell plain\">completion, config, create, ddp, dedupe, deprecate,</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number8 index7 alt1\"><code class=\"powershell spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"powershell plain\">dist</code><code class=\"powershell keyword\">-tag</code><code class=\"powershell plain\">, docs, doctor, edit, explore, get, help,</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number9 index8 alt2\"><code class=\"powershell spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"powershell plain\">help</code><code class=\"powershell keyword\">-search</code><code class=\"powershell plain\">, hook, i, init, install, install</code><code class=\"powershell keyword\">-test</code><code class=\"powershell plain\">, it, link,</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number10 index9 alt1\"><code class=\"powershell spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"powershell plain\">list, ln, login, logout, </code><code class=\"powershell keyword\">ls</code><code class=\"powershell plain\">, outdated, owner, pack, ping,</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number11 index10 alt2\"><code class=\"powershell spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"powershell plain\">prefix, profile, prune, publish, rb, rebuild, repo, restart,</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number12 index11 alt1\"><code class=\"powershell spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"powershell plain\">root, run, run</code><code class=\"powershell keyword\">-script</code><code class=\"powershell plain\">, s, se, search, </code><code class=\"powershell keyword\">set</code><code class=\"powershell plain\">, shrinkwrap, star,</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number13 index12 alt2\"><code class=\"powershell spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"powershell plain\">stars, start, stop, t, team, test, token, tst, un,</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number14 index13 alt1\"><code class=\"powershell spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"powershell plain\">uninstall, unpublish, unstar, up, update, v, version, view,</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number15 index14 alt2\"><code class=\"powershell spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"powershell plain\">whoami</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number16 index15 alt1\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number17 index16 alt2\"><code class=\"powershell plain\">npm &lt;command&gt; </code><code class=\"powershell keyword\">-h</code>&nbsp; <code class=\"powershell plain\">quick help on &lt;command&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number18 index17 alt1\"><code class=\"powershell plain\">npm </code><code class=\"powershell keyword\">-l</code>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <code class=\"powershell plain\">display full usage info</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number19 index18 alt2\"><code class=\"powershell plain\">npm help &lt;term&gt;&nbsp;&nbsp; search for help on &lt;term&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number20 index19 alt1\"><code class=\"powershell plain\">npm help npm&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; involved overview</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number21 index20 alt2\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number22 index21 alt1\"><code class=\"powershell plain\">Specify configs in the ini</code><code class=\"powershell keyword\">-formatted</code> <code class=\"powershell plain\">file:</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number23 index22 alt2\"><code class=\"powershell spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"powershell plain\">C:\\Users\\Editorial\\.npmrc</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number24 index23 alt1\"><code class=\"powershell plain\">or on the command line via: npm &lt;command&gt; -</code><code class=\"powershell keyword\">-key</code> <code class=\"powershell plain\">value</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number25 index24 alt2\"><code class=\"powershell plain\">Config info can be viewed via: npm help config</code></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"code-caption\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Listagem 1</strong>. Comandos NPM</div>\r\n<div class=\"code-caption\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>Atrav&eacute;s do NPM iremos instalar o gerenciador de depend&ecirc;ncias do Facebook Yarn, que &eacute; mais recomendado para se trabalhar usando o React. Iremos instalar o Yarn globalmente pelo NPM, como ilustra a&nbsp;<strong>Listagem 2</strong>.</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-area\">\r\n<div class=\"pre_js code-sample\">\r\n<div><code class=\"code-sample\"></code>\r\n<div>\r\n<div id=\"highlighter_881773\" class=\"syntaxhighlighter  js\">\r\n<table style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"gutter\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\">1</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td class=\"code\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\"><code class=\"js plain\">npm install -g yarn</code></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"code-caption\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Listagem 2</strong>. Instalando Yarn</div>\r\n<div class=\"code-caption\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>Com o Node, o NPM e o Yarn instalados falta apenas um editor de texto para desenvolver a nossa aplica&ccedil;&atilde;o. Neste tutorial ser&aacute; usado o editor Open Source, Microsoft Visual Studio Code que pode ser baixado&nbsp;<a title=\"Visual Studio Code\" href=\"https://code.visualstudio.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">neste link</a>, por&eacute;m voc&ecirc; pode usar o que preferir.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>Criando o Projeto</h3>\r\n<p>Agora que nosso ambiente est&aacute; devidamente configurado, iremos criar o nosso primeiro projeto em React. Para isso primeiro precisamos instalar a ferramenta de linha de comando&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">create-react-app</span>&nbsp;que tamb&eacute;m foi desenvolvida pelo Facebook cria para n&oacute;s um projeto do zero sem nos preocuparmos com bundling, otimiza&ccedil;&atilde;o de arquivo e outros detalhes de configura&ccedil;&atilde;o que podem ser extensos quando realizados manualmente.</p>\r\n<p>Para instalar o create-react-app digite o comando ilustrado na&nbsp;<strong>Listagem 3</strong>&nbsp;em seu terminal:</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-area\">\r\n<div class=\"pre_js code-sample\">\r\n<div><code class=\"code-sample\"></code>\r\n<div>\r\n<div id=\"highlighter_21160\" class=\"syntaxhighlighter  js\">\r\n<table style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"gutter\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\">1</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td class=\"code\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\"><code class=\"js plain\">npm install -g create-react-app </code></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"code-caption\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Listagem 3</strong>. Instalando create-react-app</div>\r\n<div class=\"code-caption\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>Quando a instala&ccedil;&atilde;o terminar, o comando create-react-app vai estar dispon&iacute;vel em seu terminal e a partir dele podemos criar o projeto da nossa aplica&ccedil;&atilde;o. V&aacute; ent&atilde;o at&eacute; uma pasta adequada do seu computador pelo terminal e digite o comando da&nbsp;<strong>Listagem 4</strong>;</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-area\">\r\n<div class=\"pre_js code-sample\">\r\n<div><code class=\"code-sample\"></code>\r\n<div>\r\n<div id=\"highlighter_804600\" class=\"syntaxhighlighter  js\">\r\n<table style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"gutter\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\">1</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td class=\"code\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\"><code class=\"js plain\">create-react-app meu-app-react&nbsp; </code></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"code-caption\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Listagem 4</strong>. Criando o app React</div>\r\n<div class=\"code-caption\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>O processo de cria&ccedil;&atilde;o do projeto pode levar alguns instantes enquanto&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">create-react-app</span>&nbsp;monta todo o boilerplate m&iacute;nimo que uma aplica&ccedil;&atilde;o React para a web precisa ter.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>Explorando a aplica&ccedil;&atilde;o</h3>\r\n<p>Agora que o projeto da nossa aplica&ccedil;&atilde;o foi criado iremos explorar um pouco dos seus arquivos e do c&oacute;digo fonte b&aacute;sico que foi gerado pelo&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">create-react-app</span>.</p>\r\n<p>Antes de qualquer coisa entre com o terminal na pasta que&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">create-react-app</span>&nbsp;criou e digite o comando contido na&nbsp;<strong>Listagem 5</strong>&nbsp;para executar a aplica&ccedil;&atilde;o no navegador.</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-area\">\r\n<div class=\"pre_js code-sample\">\r\n<div><code class=\"code-sample\"></code>\r\n<div>\r\n<div id=\"highlighter_289571\" class=\"syntaxhighlighter  js\">\r\n<table style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"gutter\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\">1</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td class=\"code\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\"><code class=\"js plain\">yarn start </code></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"code-caption\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Listagem 5</strong>. Executando a aplica&ccedil;&atilde;o</div>\r\n<div class=\"code-caption\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>Ap&oacute;s terminar de carregar, o projeto ser&aacute; servido localmente em seu computador na porta 3000 e o navegador definido como padr&atilde;o em seu sistema operacional ir&aacute; abrir a p&aacute;gina da aplica&ccedil;&atilde;o automaticamente, a&nbsp;<strong>Figura 2</strong>&nbsp;mostra a tela inicial padr&atilde;o criada pelo&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">create-react-app</span>.</p>\r\n<figure class=\"lazy-img\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"imagem_artigo loaded\" style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://arquivo.devmedia.com.br/artigos/criando_projeto_react_40329/pagina_aplicacao.png\" alt=\"P&aacute;gina inicial do React\" width=\"589\" height=\"549\" />\r\n<figcaption><strong>Figura 2</strong>. P&aacute;gina inicial do React<br /><br /></figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<p>Dentro do projeto voc&ecirc; ir&aacute; encontrar tr&ecirc;s pastas, cada qual ter&aacute; uma s&eacute;rie de arquivos que &eacute; utilizado de alguma forma pela aplica&ccedil;&atilde;o React:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"lf-badge\">node_modules</span>&nbsp;- Pasta respons&aacute;vel por guardar todas as depend&ecirc;ncias do projeto. Essa pasta &eacute; criada pelo NPM ou pelo Yarn no momento em que uma biblioteca, como o pr&oacute;prio React, &eacute; adicionada ao projeto.</li>\r\n<li><span class=\"lf-badge\">public</span>&nbsp;- Pasta p&uacute;blica da aplica&ccedil;&atilde;o web. Nela ficam guardados os arquivos iniciais da aplica&ccedil;&atilde;o, como o index.html que &eacute; interpretado pelo navegador, o &iacute;cone do site e um arquivo JSON com os par&acirc;metros de configura&ccedil;&atilde;o do site.</li>\r\n<li><span class=\"lf-badge\">src</span>&nbsp;- C&oacute;digo fonte da aplica&ccedil;&atilde;o: Aqui ficar&atilde;o todos os arquivos JavaScript que ir&atilde;o compor a nossa aplica&ccedil;&atilde;o.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>O pr&oacute;ximo passo ser&aacute; abrir a pasta do projeto com o seu editor de texto favorito em seguida abra a pasta&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">src</span>&nbsp;que cont&eacute;m todo o C&oacute;digo fonte da nossa aplica&ccedil;&atilde;o. Nesta pasta abra o arquivo&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">App.js</span>&nbsp;que ir&aacute; conter o c&oacute;digo descrito na&nbsp;<strong>Listagem 6</strong>.</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-area\">\r\n<div class=\"pre_js code-sample\">\r\n<div><code class=\"code-sample\"></code>\r\n<div>\r\n<div id=\"highlighter_918613\" class=\"syntaxhighlighter  js\">\r\n<table style=\"width: 633px; height: 802px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"gutter\" style=\"width: 32.9167px;\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\">1</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\">2</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\">3</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number4 index3 alt1\">4</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number5 index4 alt2\">5</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number6 index5 alt1\">6</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number7 index6 alt2\">7</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number8 index7 alt1\">8</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number9 index8 alt2\">9</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number10 index9 alt1\">10</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number11 index10 alt2\">11</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number12 index11 alt1\">12</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number13 index12 alt2\">13</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number14 index13 alt1\">14</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number15 index14 alt2\">15</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number16 index15 alt1\">16</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number17 index16 alt2\">17</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number18 index17 alt1\">18</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number19 index18 alt2\">19</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number20 index19 alt1\">20</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number21 index20 alt2\">21</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number22 index21 alt1\">22</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number23 index22 alt2\">23</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number24 index23 alt1\">24</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number25 index24 alt2\">25</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number26 index25 alt1\">26</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number27 index26 alt2\">27</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number28 index27 alt1\">28</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td class=\"code\" style=\"width: 564.028px;\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\"><code class=\"js plain\">import React, { Component } from </code><code class=\"js string\">\'react\'</code><code class=\"js plain\">;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\"><code class=\"js plain\">import logo from </code><code class=\"js string\">\'./logo.svg\'</code><code class=\"js plain\">;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\"><code class=\"js plain\">import </code><code class=\"js string\">\'./App.css\'</code><code class=\"js plain\">;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number4 index3 alt1\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number5 index4 alt2\"><code class=\"js plain\">class App extends Component {</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number6 index5 alt1\"><code class=\"js spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"js plain\">render() {</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number7 index6 alt2\"><code class=\"js spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"js keyword\">return</code> <code class=\"js plain\">(</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number8 index7 alt1\"><code class=\"js spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"js plain\">&lt;div className=</code><code class=\"js string\">\"App\"</code><code class=\"js plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number9 index8 alt2\"><code class=\"js spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"js plain\">&lt;header className=</code><code class=\"js string\">\"App-header\"</code><code class=\"js plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number10 index9 alt1\"><code class=\"js spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"js plain\">&lt;img src={logo} className=</code><code class=\"js string\">\"App-logo\"</code> <code class=\"js plain\">alt=</code><code class=\"js string\">\"logo\"</code> <code class=\"js plain\">/&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number11 index10 alt2\"><code class=\"js spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"js plain\">&lt;p&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number12 index11 alt1\"><code class=\"js spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"js plain\">Edit &lt;code&gt;src/App.js&lt;/code&gt; and save to reload.</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number13 index12 alt2\"><code class=\"js spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"js plain\">&lt;/p&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number14 index13 alt1\"><code class=\"js spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"js plain\">&lt;a</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number15 index14 alt2\"><code class=\"js spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"js plain\">className=</code><code class=\"js string\">\"App-link\"</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number16 index15 alt1\"><code class=\"js spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"js plain\">href=</code><code class=\"js string\">\"<a href=\"https://reactjs.org/\">https://reactjs.org</a>\"</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number17 index16 alt2\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><code class=\"js spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"js plain\">target=</code><code class=\"js string\">\"_blank\"</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number18 index17 alt1\"><code class=\"js spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"js plain\">rel=</code><code class=\"js string\">\"noopener noreferrer\"</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number19 index18 alt2\"><code class=\"js spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"js plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number20 index19 alt1\"><code class=\"js spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"js plain\">Learn React</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number21 index20 alt2\"><code class=\"js spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"js plain\">&lt;/a&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number22 index21 alt1\"><code class=\"js spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"js plain\">&lt;/header&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number23 index22 alt2\"><code class=\"js spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"js plain\">&lt;/div&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number24 index23 alt1\"><code class=\"js spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"js plain\">);</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number25 index24 alt2\"><code class=\"js spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"js plain\">}</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number26 index25 alt1\"><code class=\"js plain\">}</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number27 index26 alt2\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number28 index27 alt1\"><code class=\"js plain\">export </code><code class=\"js keyword\">default</code> <code class=\"js plain\">App;</code></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"code-caption\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Listagem 6</strong>. App.js criado automaticamente</div>\r\n<div class=\"code-caption\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>Em um primeiro momento voc&ecirc; pode estranhar o c&oacute;digo html sendo retornado pelo m&eacute;todo render da classe App. Essa sintaxe &eacute; chamada JSX (JavaScript and XML) e permite interagir com a template do nosso site diretamente com o JavaScript sem precisar aprender uma nova linguagem.</p>\r\n<p>Iremos ent&atilde;o escrever \"Ol&aacute; mundo\" neste componente: apague o c&oacute;digo sendo retornado pelo m&eacute;todo render deixando apenas a&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">div</span>&nbsp;que possui o&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">className</span>&nbsp;\"<span class=\"lf-badge\">App</span>\" e o header para manter o estilo. Dentro do header crie um&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">h1</span>&nbsp;com o nosso Ol&aacute; mundo, como mostrado na&nbsp;<strong>Listagem 7</strong>;</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-area\">\r\n<div class=\"pre_js code-sample\">\r\n<div><code class=\"code-sample\"></code>\r\n<div>\r\n<div id=\"highlighter_946643\" class=\"syntaxhighlighter  js\">\r\n<table style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"gutter\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\">1</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\">2</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\">3</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number4 index3 alt1\">4</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number5 index4 alt2\">5</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number6 index5 alt1\">6</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number7 index6 alt2\">7</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number8 index7 alt1\">8</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number9 index8 alt2\">9</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number10 index9 alt1\">10</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number11 index10 alt2\">11</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number12 index11 alt1\">12</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number13 index12 alt2\">13</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number14 index13 alt1\">14</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number15 index14 alt2\">15</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number16 index15 alt1\">16</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number17 index16 alt2\">17</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td class=\"code\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\"><code class=\"js plain\">import React, { Component } from </code><code class=\"js string\">\'react\'</code><code class=\"js plain\">;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\"><code class=\"js plain\">import logo from </code><code class=\"js string\">\'./logo.svg\'</code><code class=\"js plain\">;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\"><code class=\"js plain\">import </code><code class=\"js string\">\'./App.css\'</code><code class=\"js plain\">;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number4 index3 alt1\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number5 index4 alt2\"><code class=\"js plain\">class App extends Component {</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number6 index5 alt1\"><code class=\"js spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"js plain\">render() {</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number7 index6 alt2\"><code class=\"js spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"js keyword\">return</code> <code class=\"js plain\">(</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number8 index7 alt1\"><code class=\"js spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"js plain\">&lt;div className=</code><code class=\"js string\">\"App\"</code><code class=\"js plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number9 index8 alt2\"><code class=\"js spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"js plain\">&lt;header className=</code><code class=\"js string\">\"App-header\"</code><code class=\"js plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number10 index9 alt1\"><code class=\"js spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"js plain\">&lt;h1&gt;Ol&aacute; Mundo!&lt;/h1&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number11 index10 alt2\"><code class=\"js spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"js plain\">&lt;/header&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number12 index11 alt1\"><code class=\"js spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"js plain\">&lt;/div&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number13 index12 alt2\"><code class=\"js spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"js plain\">);</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number14 index13 alt1\"><code class=\"js spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"js plain\">}</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number15 index14 alt2\"><code class=\"js plain\">}</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number16 index15 alt1\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number17 index16 alt2\"><code class=\"js plain\">export </code><code class=\"js keyword\">default</code> <code class=\"js plain\">App;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </code></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"code-caption\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Listagem 7</strong>. Ol&aacute; Mundo!</div>\r\n<div class=\"code-caption\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>Ap&oacute;s salvar o arquivo alterado repare que a p&aacute;gina no navegador ser&aacute; atualizada automaticamente e voc&ecirc; ver&aacute; uma tela parecida com a da&nbsp;<strong>Figura 3</strong>.</p>\r\n<figure class=\"lazy-img\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"imagem_artigo loaded\" style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://arquivo.devmedia.com.br/artigos/criando_projeto_react_40329/ola_mundo.png\" alt=\"Ol&aacute; Mundo!\" width=\"459\" height=\"441\" />\r\n<figcaption><strong>Figura 3</strong>. Ol&aacute; Mundo!<br /><br /></figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<h3>Conclus&atilde;o</h3>\r\n<p>Voc&ecirc; acabou de dar o seu primeiro passo no desenvolvimento web com React, mas a sua jornada est&aacute; s&oacute; come&ccedil;ando. React &eacute; uma ferramenta poderos&iacute;ssima com a qual diversos sistemas complexos, como o Facebook, Netflix e Spotify, foram criados. A partir daqui voc&ecirc; est&aacute; pronto para criar o seu primeiro componente e aprender como o React trabalha para criar aplica&ccedil;&otilde;es vastas com uma rica experi&ecirc;ncia de usu&aacute;rios.</p>\r\n</section>\r\n</section>','2020-02-10 16:43:32','2020-02-22 08:47:46',2),(4,'Como instalar React-Native no Windows','Como-instalar-React-Native-no-Windows','<header class=\"postHeader\">\r\n<h1 class=\"postHeaderTitle\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Windows</h1>\r\n</header>\r\n<article>\r\n<div>\r\n<p><img class=\"img-fluid\" style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://docs.rocketseat.dev/assets/ambiente-react-native/Windows.png\" alt=\"Windows\" width=\"724\" height=\"301\" /></p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Instale o Chocolatey e as demais depend&ecirc;ncias:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://docs.rocketseat.dev/ambiente-react-native/android/windows#chocolatey\">Instalando chocolatey</a></li>\r\n<li>Instale e configure a SDK do Android:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://docs.rocketseat.dev/ambiente-react-native/android/windows#configurando-sdk-do-android-no-windows\">Configurando SDK</a></li>\r\n<li>Instale e configure o emulador Genymotion:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://docs.rocketseat.dev/ambiente-react-native/android/emulador\">Configurando Emulador</a></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<hr />\r\n<h2>Chocolatey</h2>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<p>Para configurar o ambiente Android no Windows, vamos precisar instalar 4 depend&ecirc;ncias:&nbsp;<strong>Node, Python2, JDK e a SDK do Android.</strong></p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<h3>Instalando Chocolatey</h3>\r\n<p>Para instalar as libs no Windows, vamos utilizar um gerenciador de pacotes do Windows chamado Chocolatey. Essa ferramenta nos possibilita instalar depend&ecirc;ncias e ferramentas no sistema com poucos comandos e tudo pelo terminal. Execute o prompt de comando ou powershell como administrador utilizando a tecla&nbsp;<kbd>Windows + X</kbd>&nbsp;ou clicando com o bot&atilde;o direito sobre o bot&atilde;o &ldquo;Iniciar&rdquo;:</p>\r\n<p><img class=\"img-fluid\" style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://docs.rocketseat.dev/assets/ambiente-react-native/prompt.png\" alt=\"Prompt\" /></p>\r\n<p>Agora, voc&ecirc; deve executar os comandos abaixo de acordo com a&nbsp;<strong>op&ccedil;&atilde;o que voc&ecirc; clicou</strong></p>\r\n<h3>Command Prompt</h3>\r\n<p>Caso a op&ccedil;&atilde;o que voc&ecirc; tenha clicado tenha o nome de&nbsp;<strong>Command Prompt</strong>, execute o comando abaixo na janela aberta para instalar o Chocolatey:</p>\r\n<pre><code class=\"hljs css language-console\"><span class=\"hljs-meta\">$</span><span class=\"bash\"> @<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"%SystemRoot%\\System32\\WindowsPowerShell\\v1.0\\powershell.exe\"</span> -NoProfile -InputFormat None -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -Command <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"iex ((New-Object System.Net.WebClient).DownloadString(\'https://chocolatey.org/install.ps1\'))\"</span> &amp;&amp; SET <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"PATH=%PATH%;%ALLUSERSPROFILE%\\chocolatey\\bin\"</span></span>\r\n</code></pre>\r\n<h3>Powershell</h3>\r\n<p>Caso a op&ccedil;&atilde;o tenha sido&nbsp;<strong>Powershell</strong>, execute o comando abaixo para verificar se voc&ecirc; possui permiss&otilde;es para instalar depend&ecirc;ncias com o terminal:</p>\r\n<pre><code class=\"hljs css language-console\"><span class=\"hljs-meta\">$</span><span class=\"bash\"> Get-ExecutionPolicy</span>\r\n</code></pre>\r\n<p><strong>Se</strong>&nbsp;o retorno desse comando for&nbsp;<strong>&ldquo;Restricted&rdquo;</strong>, execute o pr&oacute;ximo comando em seu terminal, se n&atilde;o, prossiga para o pr&oacute;ximo passo:</p>\r\n<pre><code class=\"hljs css language-console\"><span class=\"hljs-meta\">$</span><span class=\"bash\"> Set-ExecutionPolicy AllSigned</span>\r\n</code></pre>\r\n<p>Agora, execute o seguinte comando para instalar o Chocolatey:</p>\r\n<pre><code class=\"hljs css language-console\"><span class=\"hljs-meta\">$</span><span class=\"bash\"> Set-ExecutionPolicy Bypass -Scope Process -Force; iex ((New-Object System.Net.WebClient).DownloadString(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\'https://chocolatey.org/install.ps1\'</span>))</span>\r\n</code></pre>\r\n<p>Agora, teste se a instala&ccedil;&atilde;o ocorreu corretamente executando o seguinte comando no seu terminal (nada ir&aacute; acontecer, mas n&atilde;o deve retornar erros). Nesse passo pode ser necess&aacute;rio reiniciar seu terminal.</p>\r\n<pre><code class=\"hljs css language-console\"><span class=\"hljs-meta\">$</span><span class=\"bash\"> choco</span>\r\n</code></pre>\r\n<p>Agora vamos instalar o Node, Python2 e a JDK8 (Java Development Kit 8).</p>\r\n<pre><code class=\"hljs css language-console\"><span class=\"hljs-meta\">$</span><span class=\"bash\"> choco install -y nodejs.install python2 jdk8</span>\r\n</code></pre>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<p>Se voc&ecirc; tiver o NodeJS j&aacute; instalado em sua m&aacute;quina, certifique-se que sua vers&atilde;o &eacute; superior &agrave; 7 e caso esteja com o JDK instalado em sua m&aacute;quina, certifique-se que sua vers&atilde;o seja a 8.</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p>Agora com as depend&ecirc;ncias instaladas, vamos instalar o CLI (Command Line Interface) do React Native que nos ajudar&aacute; na cria&ccedil;&atilde;o e teste de novos projetos. Nesse passo voc&ecirc; provavelmente deve reiniciar seu terminal para o comando funcionar.</p>\r\n<pre><code class=\"hljs css language-console\"><span class=\"hljs-meta\">$</span><span class=\"bash\"> npm install -g react-native-cli</span>\r\n\r\n// ou yarn global add react-native-cli\r\n</code></pre>\r\n<p>Se tudo ocorreu bem at&eacute; aqui, voc&ecirc; conseguir&aacute; executar o seguinte comando:</p>\r\n<pre><code class=\"hljs css language-console\"><span class=\"hljs-meta\">$</span><span class=\"bash\"> react-native -h</span>\r\n</code></pre>\r\n<p>Esse comando deve exibir uma lista de comandos poss&iacute;veis para serem executados com o React Native CLI.</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<h2>Configurando SDK do Android no Windows</h2>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://docs.rocketseat.dev/assets/android-studio.png\" alt=\"Android\" /></p>\r\n<p>Crie uma pasta em um local desejado para instala&ccedil;&atilde;o da SDK. Ex:&nbsp;<code>C:\\Android\\Sdk</code></p>\r\n<p><strong>Anote esse caminho para ser utilizado posteriormente</strong></p>\r\n<p>Acesse&nbsp;<a href=\"https://developer.android.com/studio/#downloads\">https://developer.android.com/studio/#downloads</a>, na op&ccedil;&atilde;o \"Command line tools only\" baixe a SDK referente ao seu sistema operacional.</p>\r\n<p>Ap&oacute;s feito o Download, extraia o conte&uacute;do do pacote para a pasta criada no passo anterior.</p>\r\n<p>Agora, no Painel de Controle do Windows, abra o item &ldquo;Sistema e Seguran&ccedil;a&rdquo; ou &ldquo;Sistema&rdquo;, clique em &ldquo;Configura&ccedil;&otilde;es avan&ccedil;adas do sistema&rdquo;, selecione &ldquo;Vari&aacute;veis de ambiente&rdquo; e clique no bot&atilde;o &ldquo;Nova vari&aacute;vel de ambiente&rdquo;, indique o nome da vari&aacute;vel como ANDROID_HOME, adicione o caminho utilizado acima (Ex:&nbsp;<code>C:\\Android\\Sdk</code>) como segundo par&acirc;metro e clique em OK.</p>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://docs.rocketseat.dev/assets/ambiente-react-native/5.png\" alt=\"Prompt\" /></p>\r\n<p>Na mesma janela de \"Vari&aacute;veis de ambiente\" no Windows, clique na vari&aacute;vel PATH e ent&atilde;o em \"Editar\". Haver&aacute; uma lista de caminhos e voc&ecirc; deve adicionar esses dois novos caminhos no fim da lista:</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li><code>%ANDROID_HOME%\\platform-tools</code></li>\r\n<li><code>%ANDROID_HOME%\\tools</code></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<p><strong>Se sua vers&atilde;o do Windows for menor que a 10 sempre coloque ponto-e-virgula \";\" no final dos caminhos para eles n&atilde;o se juntarem</strong></p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p>Agora, abra seu Command Prompt ou PowerShell como administrador e execute o seguinte comando:</p>\r\n<p><em>Command Prompt</em></p>\r\n<pre><code class=\"hljs css language-console\"><span class=\"hljs-meta\">$</span><span class=\"bash\"> C:\\Android\\Sdk\\tools\\bin\\sdkmanager  <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"platform-tools\"</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"platforms;android-27\"</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"build-tools;27.0.3\"</span></span>\r\n</code></pre>\r\n<p><em>PowerShell</em></p>\r\n<pre><code class=\"hljs css language-console\"><span class=\"hljs-meta\">$</span><span class=\"bash\"> PS C:\\Android\\Sdk\\tools\\bin&gt; .\\sdkmanager.bat  <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"platform-tools\"</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"platforms;android-27\"</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"build-tools;27.0.3\"</span></span>\r\n</code></pre>\r\n<p><em>*Aceite todas licen&ccedil;as digitando&nbsp;<kbd>y</kbd>&nbsp;quando necess&aacute;rio.</em></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</article>','2020-02-10 16:46:17','2020-02-28 11:51:11',3),(5,'O que é e como funciona a linguagem JavaScript?','O-que-e-e-como-funciona-a-linguagem-JavaScript','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Houve um tempo em que a internet era uma coisa est&aacute;tica, chata e sem vida. Em seus prim&oacute;rdios, a World Wide Web era apenas um grande aglomerado de p&aacute;ginas HTML com links que apontavam uns para os outros e nada mais. Com o passar dos anos, as necessidades de quem navegava na internet foram ficando cada vez mais complexas e exigiam uma forma mais avan&ccedil;ada das p&aacute;ginas web interagirem com os navegadores e seus usu&aacute;rios.</p>\r\n<div class=\"continua-apos-publicidade\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hoje, a realidade &eacute; completamente diferente. A internet n&atilde;o &eacute; mais composta por meros documentos HTML com um punhado de texto e imagens, mas sim por aplica&ccedil;&otilde;es completas e funcionais que facilitam enormemente o dia-a-dia de todos. E tudo isso gra&ccedil;as ao surgimento de uma certa tecnologia que est&aacute; presente em nossa vida digital, mesmo que sequer nos demos conta disso: o&nbsp;<a class=\"termo\" href=\"https://canaltech.com.br/internet/O-que-e-e-como-funciona-a-linguagem-JavaScript/\">JavaScript</a>.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Essa linguagem de programa&ccedil;&atilde;o n&atilde;o foi projetada para rodar em servidores (como linguagens mais tradicionais), mas no navegador do usu&aacute;rio. Ignorada por alguns e subestimada por outros (houve um tempo em que ela foi considerada uma \"linguagem de brinquedo\"), atualmente n&atilde;o h&aacute; um site sequer que n&atilde;o a use e os incr&iacute;veis avan&ccedil;os da WWW (aplica&ccedil;&otilde;es ricas, atualiza&ccedil;&atilde;o din&acirc;mica de conte&uacute;do, etc) seriam imposs&iacute;veis sem ela.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h4>O que &eacute; JavaScript?</h4>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">JavaScript &eacute; uma linguagem de programa&ccedil;&atilde;o criada em 1995 por Brendan Eich enquanto trabalhava na Netscape Communications Corporation. Originalmente projetada para rodar no Netscape Navigator, ela tinha o prop&oacute;sito de oferecer aos desenvolvedores formas de tornar determinados processos de p&aacute;ginas web mais din&acirc;micos, tornando seu uso mais agrad&aacute;vel. Um ano depois de seu lan&ccedil;amento, a&nbsp;<a class=\"linkagem\" title=\"Ir para tudo sobre Microsoft\" href=\"https://canaltech.com.br/empresa/microsoft/\">Microsoft</a>&nbsp;portou a linguagem para seu navegador, o que ajudou a consolidar a linguagem e torn&aacute;-la uma das tecnologias mais importantes e utilizadas na internet.</p>\r\n<div class=\"player_dynad_tv\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Embora ela tenha esse nome, n&atilde;o se deve confundir JavaScript com Java, linguagem de programa&ccedil;&atilde;o desenvolvida pela Sun Microsystems: antes, a linguagem criada pela Netscape recebera nomes como LiveScript e Mocha, mas, para aproveitar o grande sucesso da linguagem da Sun no mercado, os executivos da Netscape resolveram mudar o nome de sua linguagem para o atual. Entretanto, Java e Java Script s&atilde;o completamente diferentes e possuem prop&oacute;sitos diversos.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<figure class=\"image align-center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img style=\"width: 567px; height: 265px;\" title=\"Exemplo de JavaScript\" src=\"https://imagens.canaltech.com.br/78549.122265-Exemplo-de-JavaScript.jpg\" alt=\"Exemplo de JavaScript\" width=\"612\" height=\"285\" />\r\n<figcaption></figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mas como o JavaScript funciona? Ao inv&eacute;s de rodar remotamente em servidores na internet, o JavaScript tem como caracter&iacute;stica rodar programas localmente - do lado do cliente, como se costuma dizer em TI. Assim sendo, o JavaScript fornece &agrave;s p&aacute;ginas web a possibilidade de programa&ccedil;&atilde;o, transforma&ccedil;&atilde;o e processamento de dados enviados e recebidos, interagindo com a marca&ccedil;&atilde;o e exibi&ccedil;&atilde;o de conte&uacute;do da linguagem HTML e com a estiliza&ccedil;&atilde;o desse conte&uacute;do proporcionada pelo CSS nessas p&aacute;ginas.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Scripts de c&oacute;digo escritos nessa linguagem e executados em um navegador permitem, por exemplo, atualizar parte do conte&uacute;do de uma p&aacute;gina web sem carreg&aacute;-la totalmente ap&oacute;s preencher um formul&aacute;rio, atrav&eacute;s de t&eacute;cnicas de programa&ccedil;&atilde;o como o AJAX. Isso permite a cria&ccedil;&atilde;o de uma infinidade de softwares completos e totalmente funcionais para diversas finalidades. O Google Docs jamais funcionaria sem a exist&ecirc;ncia do JavaScript, por exemplo.</p>\r\n<div class=\"continua-apos-publicidade\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h4>JavaScript hoje</h4>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Com o grande sucesso do JavaScript, tal tecnologia evoluiu para atender &agrave;s mais diversas demandas que surgiam com a evolu&ccedil;&atilde;o da internet. Atualmente, &eacute; poss&iacute;vel n&atilde;o apenas desenvolver sites e aplicativos ricos, mas tamb&eacute;m aplicativos para smartphones e at&eacute; mesmo programas desktop. Conhe&ccedil;a agora algumas tecnologias que surgiram com a evolu&ccedil;&atilde;o do JavaScript.</p>\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: left;\">jQuery</h4>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<figure class=\"image align-center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img style=\"width: 512px; height: 161px;\" title=\"JavaScript - Tecnologias\" src=\"https://imagens.canaltech.com.br/78543.122259-JavaScript-Tecnologias.jpg\" alt=\"JavaScript - Tecnologias\" width=\"630\" height=\"198\" />\r\n<figcaption></figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">A mais famosa biblioteca JavaScript do mercado fornece uma varia&ccedil;&atilde;o dessa linguagem com uma sintaxe mais amig&aacute;vel, o que simplifica a cria&ccedil;&atilde;o de aplica&ccedil;&otilde;es. Gra&ccedil;as ao jQuery, &eacute; poss&iacute;vel escrever programas em JavaScript mais facilmente, pois a sintaxe original do JavaScript n&atilde;o &eacute; t&atilde;o f&aacute;cil de aprender.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">O jQuery se tornou t&atilde;o popular que, em muitos casos, desenvolvedores substituem totalmente o JavaScript escrito de forma nativa pelo jQuery para criar suas aplica&ccedil;&otilde;es. Muitos dos componentes din&acirc;micos que voc&ecirc; est&aacute; vendo nas p&aacute;ginas do Canaltech foram criados gra&ccedil;as a esta biblioteca.</p>\r\n<div class=\"continua-apos-publicidade\">\r\n<div id=\"banner-970x250-area\" class=\"advertisement billboard\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h4>Node.js</h4>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<figure class=\"image align-center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img style=\"width: 453px; height: 152px;\" title=\"JavaScript - Tecnologias\" src=\"https://imagens.canaltech.com.br/78545.122261-JavaScript-Tecnologias.png\" alt=\"JavaScript - Tecnologias\" width=\"630\" height=\"211\" />\r\n<figcaption></figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Embora originalmente o JavaScript tenha sido projetado para rodar em navegadores, atualmente tamb&eacute;m &eacute; poss&iacute;vel executar aplica&ccedil;&otilde;es escritos nessa linguagem em servidores web gra&ccedil;as ao Node.js.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Criado em 2009, o Node.js &eacute; um conjunto de ferramentas opensource que permite criar servidores web para execu&ccedil;&atilde;o remota de aplica&ccedil;&otilde;es JavaScript. Servi&ccedil;os importantes como&nbsp;<a class=\"linkagem\" title=\"Ir para tudo sobre PayPal\" href=\"https://canaltech.com.br/empresa/paypal/\">PayPal</a>,&nbsp;<a class=\"linkagem\" title=\"Ir para tudo sobre LinkedIn\" href=\"https://canaltech.com.br/empresa/linkedin/\">LinkedIn</a>&nbsp;e Groupon usam Node.js para funcionar.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gra&ccedil;as aos avan&ccedil;os proporcionados pela comunidade de desenvolvedores dessa ferramenta, existem implementa&ccedil;&otilde;es do Node.js at&eacute; mesmo para dispositivos da chamada Internet das Coisas: o Tessel, computador semelhante ao Arduino, executa aplica&ccedil;&otilde;es embarcadas rodando em Node.js.</p>\r\n<div class=\"continua-apos-publicidade\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h4>Desenvolvimento mobile</h4>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<figure class=\"image align-center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img style=\"width: 360px; height: 112px;\" title=\"JavaScript - Tecnologias\" src=\"https://imagens.canaltech.com.br/78547.122263-JavaScript-Tecnologias.png\" alt=\"JavaScript - Tecnologias\" width=\"581\" height=\"181\" />\r\n<figcaption></figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">O JavaScript j&aacute; transcendeu os navegadores e agora permite fazer virtualmente qualquer software que se possa imaginar, inclusive aplicativos para smartphones!</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Todos os sistemas operacionais m&oacute;veis dispon&iacute;veis no mercado suportam JavaScript, sendo poss&iacute;vel construir aplicativos para Android, iOS, Windows Phone. A vantagem aqui &eacute; que geralmente &eacute; mais f&aacute;cil desenvolver aplicativos compat&iacute;veis com todas as aplica&ccedil;&otilde;es, ao contr&aacute;rio do desenvolvimento com linguagens nativas, que limita as op&ccedil;&otilde;es ao SO de origem (Java para Android, Swift para iOS, etc).</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sencha Touch, PhoneGap, Titanium e outras tecnologias s&atilde;o apenas alguns exemplos de ferramentas que permitem a cria&ccedil;&atilde;o de poderosos aplicativos mobile com mais facilidade e flexibilidade.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h4>Possibilidades</h4>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Como se pode observar, h&aacute; muito tempo que o JavaScript se tornou mais do que uma mera linguagem para fazer truques bobos em p&aacute;ginas HTML e atualmente &eacute; praticamente imposs&iacute;vel imaginar a internet sem a exist&ecirc;ncia dele. Em conjunto com o HTML e o CSS, o JavaScript - bem como suas bibliotecas, dialetos e tecnologias relacionadas - &eacute; um dos alicerces fundamentais da web como a conhecemos.</p>\r\n<div class=\"continua-apos-publicidade\">\r\n<div id=\"banner-970x250-2-area\" class=\"advertisement billboard\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Se voc&ecirc; &eacute; aspirante a programador e deseja aprender um pouco mais sobre esta linguagem, uma dica bem bacana &eacute; participar do curso interativo oferecido pela CodeCademy - que, inclusive, jamais existiria como &eacute; hoje sem a exist&ecirc;ncia do JavaScript! A Mozilla Foundation, atual respons&aacute;vel pela linguagem, tamb&eacute;m fornece um &oacute;timo material de estudo na MDN.</p>','2020-02-25 13:01:44','2020-02-25 13:14:36',5),(6,'Introdução a Bootstrap','Introducao-a-Bootstrap','<p class=\"bd-lead\"><span>Comece com o Bootstrap, a estrutura mais popular do mundo para criar sites responsivos, primeiro para dispositivos m&oacute;veis, com o BootstrapCDN e uma p&aacute;gina inicial de modelos.</span></p>\r\n<div id=\"carbonads\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"quick-start\"><span class=\"bd-content-title\"><span>Come&ccedil;o r&aacute;pido</span></span></h2>\r\n<p><span>Deseja adicionar rapidamente o Bootstrap ao seu projeto?&nbsp;Use o BootstrapCDN, fornecido gratuitamente pelo pessoal do StackPath.&nbsp;Voc&ecirc; est&aacute; usando um gerenciador de pacotes ou precisa baixar os arquivos de origem?&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://getbootstrap.com/docs/4.4/getting-started/download/\"><span>V&aacute; para a p&aacute;gina de downloads</span></a><span>&nbsp;.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 id=\"css\"><span class=\"bd-content-title\"><span>CSS</span></span></h3>\r\n<p><span>Copie e cole a folha de estilo&nbsp;</span><code class=\"highlighter-rouge\">&lt;link&gt;</code><span>no seu&nbsp;</span><code class=\"highlighter-rouge\">&lt;head&gt;</code><span>antes de todas as outras folhas de estilo para carregar nosso CSS.</span></p>\r\n<div class=\"bd-clipboard\"><button class=\"btn-clipboard\" title=\"\" type=\"button\" data-original-title=\"Copy to clipboard\"><span>c&oacute;pia de</span></button></div>\r\n<figure class=\"highlight\">\r\n<pre><code class=\"language-html\" data-lang=\"html\"><span class=\"nt\">&lt;link</span> <span class=\"na\">rel=</span><span class=\"s\">\"stylesheet\"</span> <span class=\"na\">href=</span><span class=\"s\">\"https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.4.1/css/bootstrap.min.css\"</span> <span class=\"na\">integrity=</span><span class=\"s\">\"sha384-Vkoo8x4CGsO3+Hhxv8T/Q5PaXtkKtu6ug5TOeNV6gBiFeWPGFN9MuhOf23Q9Ifjh\"</span> <span class=\"na\">crossorigin=</span><span class=\"s\">\"anonymous\"</span><span class=\"nt\">&gt;</span></code></pre>\r\n</figure>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3 id=\"js\"><span class=\"bd-content-title\"><span>JS</span></span></h3>\r\n<p><span>Muitos de nossos componentes requerem o uso de JavaScript para funcionar.&nbsp;Especificamente, eles exigem&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://jquery.com/\"><span>jQuery</span></a><span>&nbsp;,&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://popper.js.org/\"><span>Popper.js</span></a><span>&nbsp;e nossos pr&oacute;prios plug-ins JavaScript.&nbsp;Coloque os seguintes&nbsp;</span><code class=\"highlighter-rouge\">&lt;script&gt;</code><span>s no final das suas p&aacute;ginas, logo antes da&nbsp;</span><code class=\"highlighter-rouge\">&lt;/body&gt;</code><span>tag de&nbsp;fechamento&nbsp;, para habilit&aacute;-los.&nbsp;O jQuery deve vir primeiro, depois o Popper.js e nossos plug-ins JavaScript.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Usamos&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://blog.jquery.com/2016/06/09/jquery-3-0-final-released/\"><span>o slim build do jQuery</span></a><span>&nbsp;, mas a vers&atilde;o completa tamb&eacute;m &eacute; suportada.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class=\"bd-clipboard\"><button class=\"btn-clipboard\" title=\"\" type=\"button\" data-original-title=\"Copy to clipboard\"><span>c&oacute;pia de</span></button></div>\r\n<figure class=\"highlight\">\r\n<pre><code class=\"language-html\" data-lang=\"html\"><span class=\"nt\">&lt;script </span><span class=\"na\">src=</span><span class=\"s\">\"https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.4.1.slim.min.js\"</span> <span class=\"na\">integrity=</span><span class=\"s\">\"sha384-J6qa4849blE2+poT4WnyKhv5vZF5SrPo0iEjwBvKU7imGFAV0wwj1yYfoRSJoZ+n\"</span> <span class=\"na\">crossorigin=</span><span class=\"s\">\"anonymous\"</span><span class=\"nt\">&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</span>\r\n<span class=\"nt\">&lt;script </span><span class=\"na\">src=</span><span class=\"s\">\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/popper.js@1.16.0/dist/umd/popper.min.js\"</span> <span class=\"na\">integrity=</span><span class=\"s\">\"sha384-Q6E9RHvbIyZFJoft+2mJbHaEWldlvI9IOYy5n3zV9zzTtmI3UksdQRVvoxMfooAo\"</span> <span class=\"na\">crossorigin=</span><span class=\"s\">\"anonymous\"</span><span class=\"nt\">&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</span>\r\n<span class=\"nt\">&lt;script </span><span class=\"na\">src=</span><span class=\"s\">\"https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.4.1/js/bootstrap.min.js\"</span> <span class=\"na\">integrity=</span><span class=\"s\">\"sha384-wfSDF2E50Y2D1uUdj0O3uMBJnjuUD4Ih7YwaYd1iqfktj0Uod8GCExl3Og8ifwB6\"</span> <span class=\"na\">crossorigin=</span><span class=\"s\">\"anonymous\"</span><span class=\"nt\">&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</span></code></pre>\r\n</figure>\r\n<p><span>Curioso para saber quais componentes requerem explicitamente jQuery, JS e Popper.js?&nbsp;Clique no link show components below.&nbsp;Se voc&ecirc; n&atilde;o tiver certeza da estrutura geral da p&aacute;gina, continue lendo um exemplo de modelo de p&aacute;gina.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Nosso&nbsp;</span><code class=\"highlighter-rouge\">bootstrap.bundle.js</code><span>e&nbsp;</span><code class=\"highlighter-rouge\">bootstrap.bundle.min.js</code><span>incluem&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://popper.js.org/\"><span>Popper</span></a><span>&nbsp;, mas n&atilde;o&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://jquery.com/\"><span>jQuery</span></a><span>&nbsp;.&nbsp;Para mais informa&ccedil;&otilde;es sobre o que est&aacute; inclu&iacute;do no Bootstrap, consulte nossa&nbsp;se&ccedil;&atilde;o de&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://getbootstrap.com/docs/4.4/getting-started/contents/#precompiled-bootstrap\"><span>conte&uacute;do</span></a><span>&nbsp;.</span></p>\r\n<details>\r\n<summary class=\"text-primary mb-3\"><span>Mostrar componentes que requerem JavaScript<br /><br /></span></summary>\r\n</details>\r\n<h2 id=\"starter-template\"><span class=\"bd-content-title\"><span>Modelo inicial</span></span></h2>\r\n<p><span>Certifique-se de ter suas p&aacute;ginas configuradas com os mais recentes padr&otilde;es de design e desenvolvimento.&nbsp;Isso significa usar um doctype HTML5 e incluir uma metatag de viewport para comportamentos responsivos adequados.&nbsp;Junte tudo e suas p&aacute;ginas devem ficar assim:</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class=\"bd-clipboard\"><button class=\"btn-clipboard\" title=\"\" type=\"button\" data-original-title=\"Copy to clipboard\"><span>c&oacute;pia de</span></button></div>\r\n<figure class=\"highlight\">\r\n<pre><code class=\"language-html\" data-lang=\"html\"><span class=\"cp\">&lt;!doctype html&gt;</span>\r\n<span class=\"nt\">&lt;html</span> <span class=\"na\">lang=</span><span class=\"s\">\"en\"</span><span class=\"nt\">&gt;</span>\r\n  <span class=\"nt\">&lt;head&gt;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"c\">&lt;!-- Required meta tags --&gt;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"nt\">&lt;meta</span> <span class=\"na\">charset=</span><span class=\"s\">\"utf-8\"</span><span class=\"nt\">&gt;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"nt\">&lt;meta</span> <span class=\"na\">name=</span><span class=\"s\">\"viewport\"</span> <span class=\"na\">content=</span><span class=\"s\">\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no\"</span><span class=\"nt\">&gt;</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class=\"c\">&lt;!-- Bootstrap CSS --&gt;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"nt\">&lt;link</span> <span class=\"na\">rel=</span><span class=\"s\">\"stylesheet\"</span> <span class=\"na\">href=</span><span class=\"s\">\"https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.4.1/css/bootstrap.min.css\"</span> <span class=\"na\">integrity=</span><span class=\"s\">\"sha384-Vkoo8x4CGsO3+Hhxv8T/Q5PaXtkKtu6ug5TOeNV6gBiFeWPGFN9MuhOf23Q9Ifjh\"</span> <span class=\"na\">crossorigin=</span><span class=\"s\">\"anonymous\"</span><span class=\"nt\">&gt;</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class=\"nt\">&lt;title&gt;</span>Hello, world!<span class=\"nt\">&lt;/title&gt;</span>\r\n  <span class=\"nt\">&lt;/head&gt;</span>\r\n  <span class=\"nt\">&lt;body&gt;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"nt\">&lt;h1&gt;</span>Hello, world!<span class=\"nt\">&lt;/h1&gt;</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class=\"c\">&lt;!-- Optional JavaScript --&gt;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"c\">&lt;!-- jQuery first, then Popper.js, then Bootstrap JS --&gt;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"nt\">&lt;script </span><span class=\"na\">src=</span><span class=\"s\">\"https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.4.1.slim.min.js\"</span> <span class=\"na\">integrity=</span><span class=\"s\">\"sha384-J6qa4849blE2+poT4WnyKhv5vZF5SrPo0iEjwBvKU7imGFAV0wwj1yYfoRSJoZ+n\"</span> <span class=\"na\">crossorigin=</span><span class=\"s\">\"anonymous\"</span><span class=\"nt\">&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"nt\">&lt;script </span><span class=\"na\">src=</span><span class=\"s\">\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/popper.js@1.16.0/dist/umd/popper.min.js\"</span> <span class=\"na\">integrity=</span><span class=\"s\">\"sha384-Q6E9RHvbIyZFJoft+2mJbHaEWldlvI9IOYy5n3zV9zzTtmI3UksdQRVvoxMfooAo\"</span> <span class=\"na\">crossorigin=</span><span class=\"s\">\"anonymous\"</span><span class=\"nt\">&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"nt\">&lt;script </span><span class=\"na\">src=</span><span class=\"s\">\"https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.4.1/js/bootstrap.min.js\"</span> <span class=\"na\">integrity=</span><span class=\"s\">\"sha384-wfSDF2E50Y2D1uUdj0O3uMBJnjuUD4Ih7YwaYd1iqfktj0Uod8GCExl3Og8ifwB6\"</span> <span class=\"na\">crossorigin=</span><span class=\"s\">\"anonymous\"</span><span class=\"nt\">&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</span>\r\n  <span class=\"nt\">&lt;/body&gt;</span>\r\n<span class=\"nt\">&lt;/html&gt;<br /></span></code></pre>\r\n</figure>\r\n<p><span>&Eacute; tudo o que voc&ecirc; precisa para os requisitos gerais da p&aacute;gina.&nbsp;Visite os&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://getbootstrap.com/docs/4.4/layout/overview/\"><span>documentos de layout</span></a><span>&nbsp;ou&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://getbootstrap.com/docs/4.4/examples/\"><span>nossos exemplos oficiais</span></a><span>&nbsp;para come&ccedil;ar a definir o conte&uacute;do e os componentes do seu site.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id=\"important-globals\"><span class=\"bd-content-title\"><span>Globais importantes</span></span></h2>\r\n<p><span>O Bootstrap emprega v&aacute;rios estilos e configura&ccedil;&otilde;es globais importantes que voc&ecirc; precisa conhecer ao us&aacute;-lo, todos quase exclusivamente voltados para a&nbsp;</span><em><span>normaliza&ccedil;&atilde;o</span></em><span>&nbsp;de estilos entre navegadores.&nbsp;Vamos mergulhar.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 id=\"html5-doctype\"><span class=\"bd-content-title\"><span>Doctype HTML5</span></span></h3>\r\n<p><span>O Bootstrap requer o uso do doctype HTML5.&nbsp;Sem ele, voc&ecirc; ver&aacute; alguns estilos descolados e descolados, mas inclu&iacute;-lo n&atilde;o deve causar solu&ccedil;os consider&aacute;veis.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class=\"bd-clipboard\"><button class=\"btn-clipboard\" title=\"\" type=\"button\" data-original-title=\"Copy to clipboard\"><span>c&oacute;pia de</span></button></div>\r\n<figure class=\"highlight\" style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n<pre><code class=\"language-html\" data-lang=\"html\"><span class=\"cp\">&lt;!doctype html&gt;</span>\r\n<span class=\"nt\">&lt;html</span> <span class=\"na\">lang=</span><span class=\"s\">\"en\"</span><span class=\"nt\">&gt;</span>\r\n  ...\r\n<span class=\"nt\">&lt;/html&gt;<br /></span></code></pre>\r\n</figure>\r\n<h3 id=\"responsive-meta-tag\"><span class=\"bd-content-title\"><span>Meta tag responsiva</span></span></h3>\r\n<p><span>O Bootstrap &eacute; desenvolvido&nbsp;</span><em><span>primeiro para dispositivos m&oacute;veis</span></em><span>&nbsp;, uma estrat&eacute;gia na qual otimizamos o c&oacute;digo para dispositivos m&oacute;veis e depois escalamos componentes conforme necess&aacute;rio, usando consultas de m&iacute;dia CSS.&nbsp;Para garantir a renderiza&ccedil;&atilde;o adequada e o zoom de toque em todos os dispositivos,&nbsp;</span><strong><span>adicione a metatag responsiva da viewport</span></strong><span>&nbsp;&agrave; sua&nbsp;</span><code class=\"highlighter-rouge\">&lt;head&gt;</code><span>.</span></p>\r\n<div class=\"bd-clipboard\"><button class=\"btn-clipboard\" title=\"\" type=\"button\" data-original-title=\"Copy to clipboard\"><span>c&oacute;pia de</span></button></div>\r\n<figure class=\"highlight\">\r\n<pre><code class=\"language-html\" data-lang=\"html\"><span class=\"nt\">&lt;meta</span> <span class=\"na\">name=</span><span class=\"s\">\"viewport\"</span> <span class=\"na\">content=</span><span class=\"s\">\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no\"</span><span class=\"nt\">&gt;</span></code></pre>\r\n</figure>\r\n<p><span>Voc&ecirc; pode ver um exemplo disso em a&ccedil;&atilde;o no&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://getbootstrap.com/docs/4.4/getting-started/introduction/#starter-template\"><span>modelo inicial</span></a><span>&nbsp;.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 id=\"box-sizing\"><span class=\"bd-content-title\"><span>Dimensionamento de caixa</span></span></h3>\r\n<p><span>Para um dimensionamento mais direto em CSS, trocamos o&nbsp;</span><code class=\"highlighter-rouge\">box-sizing</code><span>valor&nbsp;global&nbsp;de&nbsp;</span><code class=\"highlighter-rouge\">content-box</code><span>para&nbsp;</span><code class=\"highlighter-rouge\">border-box</code><span>.&nbsp;Isso garante&nbsp;</span><code class=\"highlighter-rouge\">padding</code><span>que n&atilde;o afeta a largura final calculada de um elemento, mas pode causar problemas com alguns softwares de terceiros, como o Google Maps e o Google Custom Search Engine.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Nas raras ocasi&otilde;es em que voc&ecirc; precisar substitu&iacute;-lo, use algo como o seguinte:</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class=\"bd-clipboard\"><button class=\"btn-clipboard\" title=\"\" type=\"button\" data-original-title=\"Copy to clipboard\"><span>c&oacute;pia de</span></button></div>\r\n<figure class=\"highlight\">\r\n<pre><code class=\"language-css\" data-lang=\"css\"><span class=\"nc\">.selector-for-some-widget</span> <span class=\"p\">{</span>\r\n  <span class=\"nl\">box-sizing</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">content-box</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"p\">}</span></code></pre>\r\n</figure>\r\n<p><span>Com o snippet acima, os elementos aninhados - incluindo o conte&uacute;do gerado via&nbsp;</span><code class=\"highlighter-rouge\">::before</code><span>e -&nbsp;</span><code class=\"highlighter-rouge\">::after</code><span>herdar&atilde;o o especificado&nbsp;</span><code class=\"highlighter-rouge\">box-sizing</code><span>para isso&nbsp;</span><code class=\"highlighter-rouge\">.selector-for-some-widget</code><span>.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Saiba mais sobre o&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://css-tricks.com/box-sizing/\"><span>modelo e o tamanho da caixa em CSS Tricks</span></a><span>&nbsp;.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 id=\"reboot\"><span class=\"bd-content-title\"><span>Reiniciar</span></span></h3>\r\n<p><span>Para uma renderiza&ccedil;&atilde;o aprimorada em v&aacute;rios navegadores, usamos&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://getbootstrap.com/docs/4.4/content/reboot/\"><span>Reinicializa&ccedil;&atilde;o</span></a><span>&nbsp;para corrigir inconsist&ecirc;ncias entre navegadores e dispositivos, fornecendo redefini&ccedil;&otilde;es ligeiramente mais opinativas para elementos HTML comuns.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id=\"community\"><span class=\"bd-content-title\"><span>Comunidade</span></span></h2>\r\n<p><span>Mantenha-se atualizado sobre o desenvolvimento do Bootstrap e entre em contato com a comunidade com esses recursos &uacute;teis.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span>Siga&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://twitter.com/getbootstrap\"><span>@getbootstrap no Twitter</span></a><span>&nbsp;.</span></li>\r\n<li><span>Leia e assine&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://blog.getbootstrap.com/\"><span>o Blog oficial do Bootstrap</span></a><span>&nbsp;.</span></li>\r\n<li><span>Junte&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://bootstrap-slack.herokuapp.com/\"><span>o quarto oficial Slack</span></a><span>&nbsp;.</span></li>\r\n<li><span>Converse com outros Bootstrappers no IRC.&nbsp;No&nbsp;</span><code class=\"highlighter-rouge\">irc.freenode.net</code><span>servidor, no&nbsp;</span><code class=\"highlighter-rouge\">##bootstrap</code><span>canal.</span></li>\r\n<li><span>A ajuda para implementa&ccedil;&atilde;o pode ser encontrada em Stack Overflow (marcado&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/tagged/bootstrap-4\"><code class=\"highlighter-rouge\">bootstrap-4</code></a><span>).</span></li>\r\n<li><span>Os desenvolvedores devem usar a palavra&nbsp;</span><code class=\"highlighter-rouge\">bootstrap</code><span>-&nbsp;chave&nbsp;nos pacotes que modificam ou aumentam a funcionalidade do Bootstrap ao distribuir por&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/search?q=keywords:bootstrap\"><span>npm</span></a><span>&nbsp;ou mecanismos de entrega semelhantes para obter a m&aacute;xima descoberta.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><span>Voc&ecirc; tamb&eacute;m pode seguir&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://twitter.com/getbootstrap\"><span>@getbootstrap no Twitter</span></a><span>&nbsp;para obter as &uacute;ltimas fofocas e v&iacute;deos musicais impressionantes.</span></p>','2020-02-25 14:03:55','2020-02-25 14:03:55',14),(7,'jQuery Tutorial','jQuery-Tutorial','<h3 id=\"Introducao\">Introdu&ccedil;&atilde;o ao jQuery</h3>\r\n<p>Nesse artigo vamos falar sobre jQuery, uma&nbsp;<strong><a title=\"Javascript Tutorial\" href=\"http://www.devmedia.com.br/javascript-tutorial/37257\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">biblioteca JavaScript</a></strong>&nbsp;desenvolvida por&nbsp;<a title=\"John Resig\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/John_Resig\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">John Resig</a>, e que se tornou uma das bibliotecas JavaScript mais populares na internet, de c&oacute;digo aberto e disponibilizada sobre as licen&ccedil;as MIT e GPL. Desse modo, &eacute; uma biblioteca que podemos utilizar para fins comerciais e pessoais, sem termos que pagar qualquer tipo de licen&ccedil;a de uso.</p>\r\n<p>Sua cria&ccedil;&atilde;o teve como foco a simplicidade e o objetivo de facilitar nossa vida no desenvolvimento de aplica&ccedil;&otilde;es que necessitariam de linhas e mais linhas de c&oacute;digo para obtermis um determinado efeito, ou efetuar uma&nbsp;<a title=\"Ajax com jQuery: Trabalhando com requisi&ccedil;&otilde;es ass&iacute;ncronas\" href=\"https://www.devmedia.com.br/ajax-com-jquery-trabalhando-com-requisicoes-assincronas/37141\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">requisi&ccedil;&atilde;o Ajax</a>. Com&nbsp;<strong>jQuery</strong>&nbsp;esse trabalho &eacute; substitu&iacute;do por poucas instru&ccedil;&otilde;es, o que faz da&nbsp;<strong>jQuery</strong>&nbsp;uma ferramenta ideal para aqueles designers e desenvolvedores com pouco conhecimento em&nbsp;<strong>JavaScript</strong>.</p>\r\n<h3 id=\"jQuery\">O que &eacute; a jQuery?</h3>\r\n<p>jQuery &eacute; uma biblioteca de fun&ccedil;&otilde;es em&nbsp;<a title=\"Guia de JavaScript\r\n\" href=\"https://www.devmedia.com.br/guia/javascript/34372\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">JavaScript</a>&nbsp;que interage com o&nbsp;<a title=\"Guia de HTML\" href=\"https://www.devmedia.com.br/guia/html/38051\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">HTML</a>, desenvolvida para simplificar os scripts interpretados no navegador do usu&aacute;rio (client-side). Criada em dezembro de 2006 no BarCamp de Nova York por&nbsp;<a title=\"John Resig About\" href=\"https://johnresig.com/about/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">John Resig</a>. Usada por cerca de 77% dos 10 mil sites mais visitados do mundo, jQuery &eacute; a mais popular das bibliotecas JavaScript.</p>\r\n<p><strong>jQuery &eacute; uma biblioteca de c&oacute;digo aberto (open source)</strong>&nbsp;e possui licen&ccedil;a dual, fazendo uso da&nbsp;<a title=\"Licen&ccedil;a MIT\" href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Licen%C3%A7a_MIT\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Licen&ccedil;a MIT</a>&nbsp;ou da&nbsp;<a title=\"GNU\" href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/GNU_General_Public_License\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">GNU General Public License</a>&nbsp;vers&atilde;o 2. A sintaxe do jQuery foi desenvolvida para simplificar a navega&ccedil;&atilde;o em documentos HTML, a sele&ccedil;&atilde;o de elementos DOM, criar anima&ccedil;&otilde;es, manipular eventos, desenvolver aplica&ccedil;&otilde;es&nbsp;<a title=\"Introdu&ccedil;&atilde;o ao AJAX\" href=\"http://www.devmedia.com.br/introducao-ao-ajax-revista-easy-java-magazine-19/24797\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">AJAX</a>&nbsp;e cria&ccedil;&atilde;o de plugins sobre ela. Permitindo aos desenvolvedores criarem camadas de abstra&ccedil;&atilde;o para intera&ccedil;&otilde;es de baixo n&iacute;vel de modo simplificado em aplica&ccedil;&otilde;es web de grande complexidade.</p>\r\n<div class=\"videoWrapper\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/FKnkPtEvfws?rel=0\" frameborder=\"0\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"></iframe></div>\r\n<p class=\"destaque-link-conteudo\" align=\"center\">Saiba mais:&nbsp;<a title=\"Curso de jQuery\" href=\"http://www.devmedia.com.br/curso/o-que-e-jquery/1973\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Curso de jQuery</a></p>\r\n<p>A jQuery &eacute; leve, seu tamanho &eacute; em torno de 30kb, extens&iacute;vel, oferece suporte a plug-ins e conta ainda com uma grande equipe de desenvolvedores que vem diariamente adicionando novos recursos e fun&ccedil;&otilde;es a est&aacute; biblioteca, nos disponibilizando uma grande quantidade de controles para interface.</p>\r\n<h3 id=\"Utilidade\">Utilidade do jQuery</h3>\r\n<p>Podemos utilizar a jQuery para:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Adicionarmos efeitos visuais e anima&ccedil;&otilde;es;</li>\r\n<li>Acessarmos e manipularmos o DOM;</li>\r\n<li>Carregarmos componentes Ajax;</li>\r\n<li>Provermos interatividade;</li>\r\n<li>Fazer altera&ccedil;&atilde;o de conte&uacute;do;</li>\r\n<li>Simplificarmos tarefas JavaScript.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 id=\"Suporte\">Suporte ao jQuery</h3>\r\n<p>A jQuery foi desenvolvida para ser uma biblioteca com suporte a qualquer navegador Web. Ela facilita a n&oacute;s desenvolvedores a muitas vezes dif&iacute;cil tarefa de desenvolvermos aplica&ccedil;&otilde;es em JavaScript, tendo que atingir a enorme quantidade de navegadores em que nossa programa&ccedil;&atilde;o poder&aacute; ser executada. Como sabemos, cada navegador possui seu pr&oacute;prio conjunto de caracter&iacute;sticas de implementa&ccedil;&atilde;o que ainda pode dificultar mais ainda, de acordo com a varia&ccedil;&atilde;o de plataforma e sistema operacional onde esteja executando. J&aacute; com a&nbsp;<strong>jQuery</strong>, nossa programa&ccedil;&atilde;o &eacute; &uacute;nica e transparente.</p>\r\n<p>Com a&nbsp;<strong>jQuery</strong>&nbsp;possu&iacute;mos suporte tamb&eacute;m &agrave;s CSS3, onde podemos&nbsp;<a title=\"CSS3 Selectors: Conhecendo os seletores das CSS3\" href=\"https://www.devmedia.com.br/css3-selectors-conhecendo-os-seletores-das-css3/24782\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">utilizar seletores CSS3</a>&nbsp;mesmo que o navegador n&atilde;o tenha suporte a esta folhas de estilo. Isso &eacute; poss&iacute;vel porque a pr&oacute;pria&nbsp;<strong>jQuery</strong>&nbsp;implementa os seletores CSS3, o que faz com que ela seja independente do navegador em que estiver sendo executada.</p>\r\n<h3 id=\"Instalacao\">Instala&ccedil;&atilde;o do jQuery</h3>\r\n<p>Podemos estar obtendo a jQuery gratuitamente no&nbsp;<a title=\"jQuery\" href=\"https://jquery.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">site</a>.</p>\r\n<figure class=\"lazy-img\"><img class=\"imagem_artigo loaded\" src=\"https://arquivo.devmedia.com.br/artigos/Ricardo_Teixeira/Introducao_jQuery/Introducao_jQuery1.jpg\" alt=\"Download da jQuery\" /><br />\r\n<figcaption><strong>Figura 1:</strong>&nbsp;Download da jQuery</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<p>Nessa p&aacute;gina inicial clique no bot&atilde;o &ldquo;download jQuery&rdquo; localizado no canto direito em laranja, como podemos ver na figura 1, e a seguinte p&aacute;gina ser&aacute; aberta.</p>\r\n<figure class=\"lazy-img\"><img class=\"imagem_artigo loaded\" src=\"https://arquivo.devmedia.com.br/artigos/Ricardo_Teixeira/Introducao_jQuery/Introducao_jQuery2.jpg\" alt=\"Escolha da vers&atilde;o para download da jQuery\" />\r\n<figcaption><strong>Figura 2:</strong>&nbsp;Escolha da vers&atilde;o para download da jQuery</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<p>Agora na p&aacute;gina de download ficamos com duas op&ccedil;&otilde;es para que voc&ecirc; escolha a que vai melhor se adequar ao seu projeto. Por&eacute;m, antes de efetuarmos o download de uma das duas, vamos conhecer a diferen&ccedil;a entre elas.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Production:</strong>&nbsp;Esta vers&atilde;o serve para ambientes de produ&ccedil;&atilde;o, &eacute; uma vers&atilde;o com o c&oacute;digo em formato compactado, sem quebra de linhas e com o c&oacute;digo sem coment&aacute;rios, possuindo apenas 15% do tamanho da que veremos a seguir.</p>\r\n<figure class=\"lazy-img\"><img class=\"imagem_artigo loaded\" src=\"https://arquivo.devmedia.com.br/artigos/Ricardo_Teixeira/Introducao_jQuery/Introducao_jQuery3.jpg\" alt=\"Vers&atilde;o production jQuery 1.9.1\" />\r\n<figcaption><strong>Figura 3:</strong>&nbsp;Vers&atilde;o production jQuery 1.9.1</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<p><strong>Development:</strong>&nbsp;Esta vers&atilde;o &eacute; para desenvolvimento, &eacute; a vers&atilde;o n&atilde;o compactada da biblioteca e possui o c&oacute;digo todo comentado. Sendo ideal para ambientes de desenvolvimento, por se integrar facilmente com as ferramentas e IDEs.</p>\r\n<figure class=\"lazy-img\"><img class=\"imagem_artigo loaded\" src=\"https://arquivo.devmedia.com.br/artigos/Ricardo_Teixeira/Introducao_jQuery/Introducao_jQuery4.jpg\" alt=\"Vers&atilde;o development jQuery 1.9.1\" />\r\n<figcaption><strong>Figura 4:</strong>&nbsp;Vers&atilde;o development jQuery 1.9.1</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<p>Agora que j&aacute; conhecemos ambas as vers&otilde;es dispon&iacute;veis, basta escolher a vers&atilde;o que desejamos usar e clicar nos links mostrados na figura 3 e na figura 4, de acordo com a vers&atilde;o escolhida para o download. A biblioteca vai abrir em formato de c&oacute;digo&nbsp;<strong>JavaScript</strong>&nbsp;no pr&oacute;prio navegador. Para salv&aacute;-la, podemos ir no meu arquivo &lt; Salvar e salvarmos na pasta de desenvolvimento ou onde preferir. Nomes recomendados para cada vers&atilde;o.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Vers&atilde;o production:&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">jquery.min.js</span>;</li>\r\n<li>Vers&atilde;o Development:&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">jquery.js</span>.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Uma dica para a melhor organiza&ccedil;&atilde;o do nosso projeto &eacute; criarmos uma pasta&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">js</span>&nbsp;dentro da pasta principal do projeto e salvar a&nbsp;<strong>jQuery</strong>&nbsp;dentro dessa pasta.</p>\r\n<h3 id=\"Incluindo\">Incluindo arquivo jQuery no HTML</h3>\r\n<p>Agora que j&aacute; fizemos o download e salvamos a jQuery dentro da pasta do nosso projeto, vamos referenciar a mesma utilizando o par&acirc;metro SRC da tag SCRIPT dentro da tag HEAD.</p>\r\n<p class=\"code-caption\"><strong>Listagem 1:</strong>&nbsp;Fazendo referencia arquivo jQuery.</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-area\">\r\n<div class=\"pre_xml code-sample\">\r\n<div><code class=\"code-sample\"></code>\r\n<div>\r\n<div id=\"highlighter_966322\" class=\"syntaxhighlighter  xml\">\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"gutter\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\">1</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\">2</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\">3</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number4 index3 alt1\">4</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number5 index4 alt2\">5</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number6 index5 alt1\">6</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td class=\"code\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\"><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">html</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\"><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">head</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">title</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;...&lt;/</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">title</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number4 index3 alt1\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml comments\">&lt;!-- Vers&atilde;o development jQuery --&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number5 index4 alt2\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">script</code> <code class=\"xml color1\">type</code><code class=\"xml plain\">=</code><code class=\"xml string\">\"text/javascript\"</code> <code class=\"xml color1\">src</code><code class=\"xml plain\">=</code><code class=\"xml string\">\"jquery.js\"</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;&lt;/</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">script</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number6 index5 alt1\"><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;/</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">head</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3 id=\"Construtor\">Construtor jQuery</h3>\r\n<p>Com a&nbsp;<strong>jQuery</strong>&nbsp;temos que utilizar a fun&ccedil;&atilde;o&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">$()</span>&nbsp;para encontrarmos um elemento HTML dentro da aplica&ccedil;&atilde;o e utilizarmos as fun&ccedil;&otilde;es da biblioteca. Essa fun&ccedil;&atilde;o [e tecnicamente conhecida como construtor ou fun&ccedil;&atilde;o construtora e ela estar&aacute; presente em todas as aplica&ccedil;&otilde;es que&nbsp;<strong>utilizarmos a jQuery</strong>.</p>\r\n<p>&Eacute; denominada desse modo para ser f&aacute;cil de decorar, e o fato de se chamar $ evita a possibilidade de ocorrer conflitos com outras fun&ccedil;&otilde;es da biblioteca do usu&aacute;rio. Ocasionalmente podemos vir a utilizar alguma outra biblioteca que tamb&eacute;m tenha como uso uma fun&ccedil;&atilde;o chamada $. Caso isso acontece podemos usar como alternativa a fun&ccedil;&atilde;o&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">jQuery()</span>.</p>\r\n<p>O construtor faz uso do seguinte par&acirc;metro, onde&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">alvo</span>&nbsp;&eacute; um seletor CSS para TAG, ID ou classe.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>$ (alvo)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Vejamos alguns exemplo de sua utiliza&ccedil;&atilde;o.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>$(&lsquo;h1&rsquo;)</li>\r\n<li>$(&lsquo;p&rsquo;)</li>\r\n<li>$(&lsquo;#conteudo&rsquo;)</li>\r\n<li>$(&lsquo;.teste&rsquo;)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Como podemos ver, no exemplo acima estamos fazendo com que a&nbsp;<strong>jQuery</strong>&nbsp;encontre os elementos, H1, P, e os elementos com&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">id=\"conte&uacute;do\"</span>&nbsp;e a&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">class=\"teste\"</span>. O requisito m&iacute;nimo para a utiliza&ccedil;&atilde;o da jQuery &eacute; saber utilizar os seletores CSS.</p>\r\n<h3 id=\"Funcao\">Fun&ccedil;&atilde;o&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">$(document).ready()</span></h3>\r\n<p>Essa fun&ccedil;&atilde;o &eacute; uma das primeiras coisas que devemos aprender na&nbsp;<strong>jQuery</strong>. De forma simples podemos dizer que essa fun&ccedil;&atilde;o &eacute; respons&aacute;vel por executar o conte&uacute;do do m&eacute;todo&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">ready()</span>, t&atilde;o logo o navegador tenha carregado todos os elementos HTML.</p>\r\n<p>O modo mais comum de utilizarmos ela &eacute; em conjunto com uma fun&ccedil;&atilde;o an&ocirc;nima, contendo os comandos que desejamos executar. Vejamos um exemplo.</p>\r\n<p class=\"code-caption\"><strong>Listagem 2:</strong>&nbsp;Fun&ccedil;&atilde;o anomina dentro da fun&ccedil;&atilde;o&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">$(document).ready()</span></p>\r\n<div class=\"code-area\">\r\n<div class=\"pre_xml code-sample\">\r\n<div><code class=\"code-sample\"></code>\r\n<div>\r\n<div id=\"highlighter_140076\" class=\"syntaxhighlighter  xml\">\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"gutter\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\">1</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\">2</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\">3</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number4 index3 alt1\">4</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number5 index4 alt2\">5</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number6 index5 alt1\">6</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number7 index6 alt2\">7</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td class=\"code\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\"><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">script</code> <code class=\"xml color1\">type</code><code class=\"xml plain\">=</code><code class=\"xml string\">\"text/javascript\"</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml plain\">$(document).ready(function(){</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number4 index3 alt1\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml plain\">//o nosso c&oacute;digo jquery vai aqui. </code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number5 index4 alt2\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number6 index5 alt1\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml plain\">});</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number7 index6 alt2\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;/</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">script</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>Vamos ent&atilde;o unir tudo que aprendemos at&eacute; agora e ver como seria o seu funcionamento na pr&aacute;tica. Para isso vamos unir todos os c&oacute;digos que geramos ate agora em um &uacute;nico arquivo e executarmos para ver se a mensagem de p&aacute;gina carregada ira realmente aparecer.</p>\r\n<p class=\"code-caption\"><strong>Listagem 4:</strong>&nbsp;Modelo jQuery completo</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-area\">\r\n<div class=\"pre_xml code-sample\">\r\n<div class=\"code-area\">\r\n<div class=\"pre_xml code-sample\">\r\n<div><code class=\"code-sample\"></code>\r\n<div>\r\n<div id=\"highlighter_334556\" class=\"syntaxhighlighter  xml\">\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"gutter\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\">1</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\">2</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\">3</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number4 index3 alt1\">4</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number5 index4 alt2\">5</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number6 index5 alt1\">6</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number7 index6 alt2\">7</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number8 index7 alt1\">8</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number9 index8 alt2\">9</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number10 index9 alt1\">10</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number11 index10 alt2\">11</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number12 index11 alt1\">12</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number13 index12 alt2\">13</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number14 index13 alt1\">14</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number15 index14 alt2\">15</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number16 index15 alt1\">16</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number17 index16 alt2\">17</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td class=\"code\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\"><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">head</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">meta</code> <code class=\"xml color1\">http-equiv</code><code class=\"xml plain\">=</code><code class=\"xml string\">\"Content-Type\"</code> <code class=\"xml color1\">content</code><code class=\"xml plain\">=</code><code class=\"xml string\">\"text/html; charset=iso-8859-1\"</code> <code class=\"xml plain\">/&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">title</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;Introdu&ccedil;&atilde;o jQuery &lt;/</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">title</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number4 index3 alt1\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml comments\">&lt;!-- Referencia a biblioteca jquery (JS) --&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number5 index4 alt2\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">script</code> <code class=\"xml color1\">type</code><code class=\"xml plain\">=</code><code class=\"xml string\">\"text/javascript\"</code> <code class=\"xml color1\">src</code><code class=\"xml plain\">=</code><code class=\"xml string\">\"jquery.js\"</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;&lt;/</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">script</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number6 index5 alt1\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml comments\">&lt;!-- Funcionalidades da p&aacute;gina --&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number7 index6 alt2\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">script</code> <code class=\"xml color1\">type</code><code class=\"xml plain\">=</code><code class=\"xml string\">\"text/javascript\"</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number8 index7 alt1\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml plain\">$(document).ready(function(){</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number9 index8 alt2\"><code class=\"xml plain\">alert(\"p&aacute;gina carregada\")</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number10 index9 alt1\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml plain\">});</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number11 index10 alt2\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;/</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">script</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number12 index11 alt1\"><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;/</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">head</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number13 index12 alt2\"><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">body</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number14 index13 alt1\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">h1</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;P&aacute;gina demonstra&ccedil;&atilde;o&lt;/</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">h1</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number15 index14 alt2\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">h2</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;jQuery biblioteca javascript.&lt;/</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">h2</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number16 index15 alt1\"><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;/</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">body</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number17 index16 alt2\"><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;/</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">html</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>Resultado:</p>\r\n<figure class=\"lazy-img\"><img class=\"imagem_artigo loaded\" src=\"https://arquivo.devmedia.com.br/artigos/Ricardo_Teixeira/Introducao_jQuery/Introducao_jQuery5.jpg\" alt=\"Exemplo p&aacute;gina usando jQuery\" />\r\n<figcaption><strong>Figura 5:</strong>&nbsp;Exemplo p&aacute;gina usando jQuery</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<p>&Eacute; importante acessar a p&aacute;gina oficial da biblioteca e consultar a documenta&ccedil;&atilde;o, bastante completa.</p>\r\n<p>Assim concluirmos mais esse artigo, espero que tenha sido do agrado e entendimento de todos os leitores. Fiquem &agrave; vontade para estar deixando sugest&otilde;es, dicas e pedidos de novos artigos.</p>\r\n<p>Um abra&ccedil;o a todos.</p>\r\n</div>','2020-02-25 14:06:18','2020-02-25 14:06:18',15),(8,'HTML básico - Códigos HTML','HTML-basico-Codigos-HTML','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ao acessar uma p&aacute;gina web atrav&eacute;s de um navegador, ele &eacute; capaz de interpretar o c&oacute;digo HTML e renderiz&aacute;-lo de forma compreens&iacute;vel para o usu&aacute;rio final, exibindo textos, bot&otilde;es etc. com as configura&ccedil;&otilde;es definidas por meio das diversas tags que essa linguagem disp&otilde;e.</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Atualmente a&nbsp;<strong>HTML</strong>&nbsp;encontra-se na vers&atilde;o 5 e &eacute; padronizada pelo W3C (World Wide Web Consortium), uma organiza&ccedil;&atilde;o internacional respons&aacute;vel por estabelecer padr&otilde;es para a internet, como a linguagem XML, CSS e o SOAP.</p>\r\n<h3 id=\"estrutura\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Estrutura b&aacute;sica de uma p&aacute;gina HTML</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">A&nbsp;<strong>estrutura b&aacute;sica de uma p&aacute;gina HTML</strong>&nbsp;pode ser vista na&nbsp;<strong>Listagem 1</strong>, na qual podemos ver as principais tags que s&atilde;o necess&aacute;rias para que o documento seja corretamente interpretado pelos browsers.</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-area\">\r\n<div class=\"pre_xml code-sample\">\r\n<div><code class=\"code-sample\"></code>\r\n<div>\r\n<div id=\"highlighter_784951\" class=\"syntaxhighlighter  xml\">\r\n<table style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"gutter\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\">1</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\">2</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\">3</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number4 index3 alt1\">4</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number5 index4 alt2\">5</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number6 index5 alt1\">6</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number7 index6 alt2\">7</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number8 index7 alt1\">8</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number9 index8 alt2\">9</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number10 index9 alt1\">10</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td class=\"code\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\"><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\"><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">html</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\"><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">head</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number4 index3 alt1\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">meta</code> <code class=\"xml color1\">charset</code><code class=\"xml plain\">=</code><code class=\"xml string\">\"UTF-8\"</code><code class=\"xml plain\">/&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number5 index4 alt2\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">title</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;Document&lt;/</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">title</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number6 index5 alt1\"><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;/</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">head</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number7 index6 alt2\"><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">body</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number8 index7 alt1\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml comments\">&lt;!-- Conte&uacute;do --&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number9 index8 alt2\"><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;/</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">body</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number10 index9 alt1\"><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;/</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">html</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"code-caption\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Listagem 1</strong>. Estrutura b&aacute;sica de uma p&aacute;gina HTML</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Linha 1</strong>: a instru&ccedil;&atilde;o&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">DOCTYPE</span>&nbsp;deve ser sempre a primeira a aparecer em uma p&aacute;gina HTML para indicar ao browser qual vers&atilde;o da linguagem usada. Nesse caso, estamos trabalhando com a HTML5, vers&atilde;o na qual a declara&ccedil;&atilde;o do DOCTYPE &eacute; bastante simples, como podemos ver na listagem;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Linhas 2</strong>&nbsp;e&nbsp;<strong>10</strong>: abertura e fechamento da tag&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">html</span>, que delimita o documento. Sendo assim, todas as demais tags da p&aacute;gina devem estar nesse espa&ccedil;o;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Linhas 3</strong>&nbsp;e&nbsp;<strong>6</strong>: abertura e fechamento da tag&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">head</span>, que define o cabe&ccedil;alho do documento. O conte&uacute;do nesse espa&ccedil;o n&atilde;o &eacute; vis&iacute;vel no browser, mas cont&eacute;m instru&ccedil;&otilde;es sobre seu conte&uacute;do e comportamento. Dentro dessa tag, por exemplo, podem ser inseridas folhas de estilo e scripts;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Linha 4</strong>: a tag&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">meta</span>, nesse caso, especifica qual conjunto de caracteres (character set ou charset) ser&aacute; usado para renderizar o texto da p&aacute;gina. O UTF-8 cont&eacute;m todos os caracteres dos padr&otilde;es Unicode e ASCII, sendo, portanto, o mais utilizado em p&aacute;ginas web. A mesma tag&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">meta</span>, por&eacute;m com outros atributos, pode ser utilizada para outros fins, como na SEO (Search Engine Optimization);</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Linha 5</strong>: a tag&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">title</span>&nbsp;define o t&iacute;tulo da p&aacute;gina, aquele que aparece na janela/aba do navegador;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Linhas 7</strong>&nbsp;e&nbsp;<strong>9</strong>: abertura e fechamento da tag&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">body</span>, marcando o espa&ccedil;o no qual deve estar contido o conte&uacute;do visual da p&aacute;gina. As demais tags que representam texto, bot&otilde;es etc. devem ser adicionadas nesse intervalo;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Linha 8</strong>: nessa linha podemos observar a sintaxe para adi&ccedil;&atilde;o de coment&aacute;rios em HTML. Esse trecho n&atilde;o &eacute; renderizado pelo browser.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Para&nbsp;<strong>desenvolver p&aacute;ginas com HTML</strong>&nbsp;basicamente precisamos de um editor de texto, como o Bloco de Notas do Windows, Nano e Emacs no Linux, entre v&aacute;rios outros. H&aacute;, ainda, editores com op&ccedil;&otilde;es avan&ccedil;adas, como recursos de syntax hilghligt e autocomplete, como Sublime Text, Atom, Brackets e Visual Studio Code, que podem ser usados para&nbsp;<strong>editar documentos HTML</strong>.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Independentemente do editor utilizado, podemos simplesmente copiar o c&oacute;digo da&nbsp;<strong>Listagem 1</strong>&nbsp;para um deles e salvar o arquivo com extens&atilde;o&nbsp;<span class=\"code-tag\">.html</span>. Em seguida, podemos abrir esse arquivo em um browser.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<h3 id=\"tags\">Tags do HTML</h3>\r\n<p>Um documento HTML &eacute; composto por tags, as quais possuem um nome e aparecem entre os sinais&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">&lt;</span>&nbsp;e&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">&gt;</span>, como vimos na&nbsp;<strong>Listagem 1</strong>, por exemplo, em&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">&lt;html&gt;</span>&nbsp;e&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">&lt;head&gt;</span>. Naquele exemplo tamb&eacute;m vimos que algumas tags precisam ser abertas e fechadas, como em&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">&lt;body&gt;</span>&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">&lt;/body&gt;</span>. Nesse caso, a tag de fechamento deve conter a barra&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">/</span>&nbsp;antes do nome. Outras, por&eacute;m, n&atilde;o precisam ser fechadas, como a tag&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">&lt;meta&gt;</span>. Nesses casos, a adi&ccedil;&atilde;o da barra&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">/</span>&nbsp;no final da pr&oacute;pria tag, como vemos na&nbsp;<strong>Linha 4</strong>&nbsp;da&nbsp;<strong>Listagem 1</strong>&nbsp;&eacute; opcional.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>Outro aspecto importante da linguagem &eacute; que ela &eacute; case insensitive, ou seja, n&atilde;o leva em considera&ccedil;&atilde;o a diferen&ccedil;a entre letras mai&uacute;sculas e min&uacute;sculas. No entanto, o uso apenas de letras min&uacute;sculas tem sido utilizado como padr&atilde;o pelos desenvolvedores.</p>\r\n<p>Al&eacute;m dessas caracter&iacute;sticas, as tags tamb&eacute;m possuem atributos, como vemos na&nbsp;<strong>Linha 4</strong>&nbsp;da&nbsp;<strong>Listagem 1</strong>, na qual a tag meta possui o atributo&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">charset=&rdquo;UTF-8&rdquo;</span>. Essas propriedades definem algumas caracter&iacute;sticas adicionais de cada tag e em alguns casos s&atilde;o obrigat&oacute;rias. Seus valores devem aparecer entre aspas duplas, como no exemplo acima, ou em aspas simples, caso o pr&oacute;prio valor contenha aspas duplas.</p>\r\n<h3 id=\"cabecalhos\">Cabe&ccedil;alhos do HTML</h3>\r\n<p>Cabe&ccedil;alhos s&atilde;o normalmente utilizados para identificar p&aacute;ginas e se&ccedil;&otilde;es e possuem apar&ecirc;ncia diferenciada do restante do texto. No HTML h&aacute; seis n&iacute;veis de cabe&ccedil;alhos/t&iacute;tulos que podem ser utilizados por meio das tags&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">h1</span>,&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">h2</span>,&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">h3</span>,&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">h4</span>,&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">h5</span>&nbsp;e&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">h6</span>, sendo&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">h1</span>&nbsp;o maior/mais relevante e&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">h6</span>&nbsp;o menor/menos relevante.</p>\r\n<div class=\"lf-nota\">De acordo com as regras de SEO, &eacute; recomendado que uma p&aacute;gina possua apenas uma tag&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">&lt;h1&gt;</span>&nbsp;que indique seu assunto, pois essa tag informa aos motores de busca qual sua principal palavra-chave.</div>\r\n<p>Na&nbsp;<strong>Listagem 2</strong>&nbsp;podemos ver como utilizar essas tags, e na&nbsp;<strong>Figura 1</strong>&nbsp;temos o resultado desse c&oacute;digo. Para testar esse c&oacute;digo, basta copi&aacute;-lo para o espa&ccedil;o indicado na&nbsp;<strong>Linha 8</strong>&nbsp;da&nbsp;<strong>Listagem 1</strong>&nbsp;e salvar o documento com a extens&atilde;o .html.</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-area\">\r\n<div class=\"pre_xml code-sample\">\r\n<div><code class=\"code-sample\"></code>\r\n<div>\r\n<div id=\"highlighter_271674\" class=\"syntaxhighlighter  xml\">\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"gutter\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\">1</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\">2</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\">3</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number4 index3 alt1\">4</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number5 index4 alt2\">5</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number6 index5 alt1\">6</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td class=\"code\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\"><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">h1</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;T&iacute;tulo de n&iacute;vel 1&lt;/</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">h1</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\"><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">h2</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;T&iacute;tulo de n&iacute;vel 2&lt;/</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">h2</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\"><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">h3</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;T&iacute;tulo de n&iacute;vel 3&lt;/</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">h3</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number4 index3 alt1\"><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">h4</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;T&iacute;tulo de n&iacute;vel 4&lt;/</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">h4</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number5 index4 alt2\"><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">h5</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;T&iacute;tulo de n&iacute;vel 5&lt;/</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">h5</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number6 index5 alt1\"><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">h6</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;T&iacute;tulo de n&iacute;vel 6&lt;/</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">h6</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"code-caption\"><strong>Listagem 2</strong>. Diferentes n&iacute;veis de cabe&ccedil;alho</div>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><a class=\"btn-run\" title=\"Show me the code\" href=\"https://jsfiddle.net/a67mo21L/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Execute o c&oacute;digo</a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<figure class=\"lazy-img\"><img class=\"loaded\" src=\"https://arquivo.devmedia.com.br/artigos/Joel_Rodrigues/HTMLBasico/compactado/htmlbasico1.png\" alt=\"Diferentes n&iacute;veis de cabe&ccedil;alho\" />\r\n<figcaption><strong>Figura 1</strong>. Diferentes n&iacute;veis de cabe&ccedil;alho</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<h3 id=\"paragrafos\">Par&aacute;grafos no HTML</h3>\r\n<p>Par&aacute;grafos de texto s&atilde;o gerados na HTML por meio das tags&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">&lt;p&gt;</span>&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">&lt;/p&gt;</span>. Esse &eacute; um exemplo de tag cuja disposi&ccedil;&atilde;o na tela se d&aacute; em forma de bloco, ou seja, um par&aacute;grafo &eacute; posto sempre abaixo do outro.</p>\r\n<p>O c&oacute;digo da&nbsp;<strong>Listagem 3</strong>&nbsp;adiciona tr&ecirc;s par&aacute;grafos, que podem ser visualizados na&nbsp;<strong>Figura 2</strong>.</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-area\">\r\n<div class=\"pre_xml code-sample\">\r\n<div><code class=\"code-sample\"></code>\r\n<div>\r\n<div id=\"highlighter_730074\" class=\"syntaxhighlighter  xml\">\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"gutter\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\">1</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\">2</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\">3</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td class=\"code\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\"><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">p</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;Primeiro par&aacute;grafo do texto.&lt;/</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">p</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\"><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">p</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;Segundo par&aacute;grafo do texto.&lt;/</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">p</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\"><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">p</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;Terceiro par&aacute;grafo do texto.&lt;/</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">p</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"code-caption\"><strong>Listagem 3</strong>. Adicionando par&aacute;grafos</div>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><a class=\"btn-run\" title=\"Show me the code\" href=\"https://jsfiddle.net/gdugd0ce/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Execute o c&oacute;digo</a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<figure class=\"lazy-img\"><img class=\"loaded\" src=\"https://arquivo.devmedia.com.br/artigos/Joel_Rodrigues/HTMLBasico/compactado/htmlbasico2.png\" alt=\"Par&aacute;grafos visualizados na p&aacute;gina\" />\r\n<figcaption><strong>Figura 2</strong>. Par&aacute;grafos visualizados na p&aacute;gina</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<h3 id=\"imagens\">Imagens no HTML</h3>\r\n<p>A inser&ccedil;&atilde;o de imagens em uma&nbsp;<strong>p&aacute;gina HTML</strong>&nbsp;pode ser feita por meio da tag&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">img</span>, que recebe no atributo&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">src</span>&nbsp;o endere&ccedil;o do arquivo a ser carregado. Al&eacute;m desse, outros dois atributos importantes s&atilde;o o&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">alt</span>, que indica um texto alternativo que ser&aacute; exibido caso o arquivo n&atilde;o possa ser carregado, e&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">title</span>, que indica o texto que aparecer&aacute; como tooltip ao passar o mouse sobre a figura.</p>\r\n<p>O c&oacute;digo da&nbsp;<strong>Listagem 4</strong>&nbsp;insere uma imagem a partir do arquivo&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">perfil.png</span>, localizado na mesma pasta do arquivo HTML, e uma tag&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">img</span>&nbsp;apontando para um arquivo inexistente. Observe na&nbsp;<strong>Figura 3</strong>&nbsp;que enquanto a primeira aparece corretamente, a segunda &eacute; exibida com um &iacute;cone de erro o texto alternativo que informamos. Note, ainda, que sobre a primeira figura est&aacute; sendo exibido o tooltip definido no atributo&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">title</span>.</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-area\">\r\n<div class=\"pre_xml code-sample\">\r\n<div><code class=\"code-sample\"></code>\r\n<div>\r\n<div id=\"highlighter_593096\" class=\"syntaxhighlighter  xml\">\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"gutter\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\">1</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\">2</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td class=\"code\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\"><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">img</code> <code class=\"xml color1\">src</code><code class=\"xml plain\">=</code><code class=\"xml string\">\"avatar.png\"</code> <code class=\"xml color1\">alt</code><code class=\"xml plain\">=</code><code class=\"xml string\">\"Texto alternativo\"</code> <code class=\"xml color1\">title</code><code class=\"xml plain\">=</code><code class=\"xml string\">\"Avatar\"</code> <code class=\"xml plain\">/&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\"><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">img</code> <code class=\"xml color1\">src</code><code class=\"xml plain\">=</code><code class=\"xml string\">\"arquivo_inexistente.jpg\"</code> <code class=\"xml color1\">alt</code><code class=\"xml plain\">=</code><code class=\"xml string\">\"Texto alternativo\"</code> <code class=\"xml color1\">title</code><code class=\"xml plain\">=</code><code class=\"xml string\">\"Outra figura\"</code><code class=\"xml plain\">/&gt;</code></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"code-caption\"><strong>Listagem 4</strong>. Inserindo imagem</div>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><a class=\"btn-run\" title=\"Show me the code\" href=\"https://jsfiddle.net/qem4rfcv/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Execute o c&oacute;digo</a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<figure class=\"lazy-img\"><img class=\"loaded\" src=\"https://arquivo.devmedia.com.br/artigos/Joel_Rodrigues/HTMLBasico/compactado/htmlbasico3.png\" alt=\"Exemplos de uso da tag img\" />\r\n<figcaption><strong>Figura 3</strong>. Exemplos de uso da tag img</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<h3 id=\"links\">Links no HTML</h3>\r\n<p>Links s&atilde;o normalmente utilizados para direcionar o usu&aacute;rio para outras p&aacute;ginas, ou para outras partes da mesma p&aacute;gina. Nos dois casos, utilizamos a tag&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">a</span>, que possui o atributo&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">href</span>&nbsp;no qual indicamos o destino daquele link.</p>\r\n<p>A&nbsp;<strong>Listagem 5</strong>&nbsp;mostra como adicionar um link para outra p&aacute;gina, neste caso, indicada pelo arquivo pagina2.html.</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-area\">\r\n<div class=\"pre_xml code-sample\">\r\n<div><code class=\"code-sample\"></code>\r\n<div>\r\n<div id=\"highlighter_583796\" class=\"syntaxhighlighter  xml\">\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"gutter\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\">1</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td class=\"code\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\"><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">a</code> <code class=\"xml color1\">href</code><code class=\"xml plain\">=</code><code class=\"xml string\">\"pagina2.html\"</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;P&aacute;gina 2&lt;/</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">a</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"code-caption\"><strong>Listagem 5</strong>. Inserindo link</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>J&aacute; a&nbsp;<strong>Listagem 6</strong>&nbsp;mostra como adicionar um link para um elemento na mesma p&aacute;gina. Nesse caso, ao clicar no link o browser mudar&aacute; o foco para o elemento que possui o atributo&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">id</span>&nbsp;igual &agrave;quele indicado no&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">href</span>.</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-area\">\r\n<div class=\"pre_xml code-sample\">\r\n<div><code class=\"code-sample\"></code>\r\n<div>\r\n<div id=\"highlighter_811392\" class=\"syntaxhighlighter  xml\">\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"gutter\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\">1</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\">2</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\">3</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td class=\"code\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\"><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">a</code> <code class=\"xml color1\">href</code><code class=\"xml plain\">=</code><code class=\"xml string\">\"#paragrafo3\"</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;Ir para o par&aacute;grafo 3&lt;/</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">a</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\"><code class=\"xml comments\">&lt;!--outros elementos--&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\"><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">p</code> <code class=\"xml color1\">id</code><code class=\"xml plain\">=</code><code class=\"xml string\">\"rodape\"</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;Par&aacute;grafo no rodap&eacute;.&lt;/p</code></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"code-caption\"><strong>Listagem 6</strong>. Inserindo link com id</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>Note tamb&eacute;m que nesse caso o&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">href</span>&nbsp;requer ainda o sinal de cerquilha (<span class=\"lf-badge\">#</span>) antes do&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">id</span>&nbsp;do elemento que ser&aacute; o foco do link.</p>\r\n<h3 id=\"tabelas\">Tabelas no HTML</h3>\r\n<p>Tabelas s&atilde;o elementos utilizados com frequ&ecirc;ncia para exibir dados de forma organizada em linhas e colunas. No HTML, elas s&atilde;o formadas por tr&ecirc;s tags b&aacute;sicas:&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">table</span>, para delimitar a tabela;&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">tr</span>, para indicar as linhas; e&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">td</span>&nbsp;para formar as colunas. A&nbsp;<strong>Listagem 7</strong>&nbsp;mostra um exemplo simples de tabela com tr&ecirc;s linhas e duas colunas, e seu resultado pode ser visto na&nbsp;<strong>Figura 4</strong>.</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-area\">\r\n<div class=\"pre_xml code-sample\">\r\n<div><code class=\"code-sample\"></code>\r\n<div>\r\n<div id=\"highlighter_399284\" class=\"syntaxhighlighter  xml\">\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"gutter\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\">1</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\">2</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\">3</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number4 index3 alt1\">4</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number5 index4 alt2\">5</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number6 index5 alt1\">6</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number7 index6 alt2\">7</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number8 index7 alt1\">8</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number9 index8 alt2\">9</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number10 index9 alt1\">10</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number11 index10 alt2\">11</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number12 index11 alt1\">12</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number13 index12 alt2\">13</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number14 index13 alt1\">14</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td class=\"code\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\"><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">table</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">tr</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">td</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;Linha 1, Coluna 1&lt;/</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">td</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number4 index3 alt1\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">td</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;Linha 1, Coluna 2&lt;/</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">td</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number5 index4 alt2\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;/</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">tr</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number6 index5 alt1\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">tr</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number7 index6 alt2\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">td</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;Linha 2, Coluna 1&lt;/</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">td</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number8 index7 alt1\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">td</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;Linha 2, Coluna 2&lt;/</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">td</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number9 index8 alt2\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;/</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">tr</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number10 index9 alt1\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">tr</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number11 index10 alt2\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">td</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;Linha 3, Coluna 1&lt;/</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">td</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number12 index11 alt1\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">td</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;Linha 3, Coluna 2&lt;/</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">td</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number13 index12 alt2\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;/</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">tr</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number14 index13 alt1\"><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;/</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">table</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"code-caption\"><strong>Listagem 7</strong>. Exemplo de uso de tabelas</div>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><a class=\"btn-run\" title=\"Show me the code\" href=\"https://jsfiddle.net/r52ud9nf/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Execute o c&oacute;digo</a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<figure class=\"lazy-img\"><img class=\"loaded\" src=\"https://arquivo.devmedia.com.br/artigos/Joel_Rodrigues/HTMLBasico/compactado/htmlbasico4.png\" alt=\"Exemplo de tabela com tr&ecirc;s linhas e duas colunas\" />\r\n<figcaption><strong>Figura 4</strong>. Exemplo de tabela com tr&ecirc;s linhas e duas colunas</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<p>Existem ainda outras tr&ecirc;s tags utilizadas para delimitar, de forma mais organizada, as partes da tabela:&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">thead</span>&nbsp;para o cabe&ccedil;alho;&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">tbody</span>&nbsp;para o corpo; e&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">tfoot</span>&nbsp;para o rodap&eacute;. A&nbsp;<strong>Listagem 8</strong>&nbsp;traz um exemplo de tabela mais complexa, utilizando todas as tags. Seu resultado &eacute; apresentado na&nbsp;<strong>Figura 5</strong>.</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-area\">\r\n<div class=\"pre_xml code-sample\">\r\n<div><code class=\"code-sample\"></code>\r\n<div>\r\n<div id=\"highlighter_472955\" class=\"syntaxhighlighter  xml\">\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"gutter\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\">1</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\">2</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\">3</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number4 index3 alt1\">4</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number5 index4 alt2\">5</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number6 index5 alt1\">6</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number7 index6 alt2\">7</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number8 index7 alt1\">8</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number9 index8 alt2\">9</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number10 index9 alt1\">10</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number11 index10 alt2\">11</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number12 index11 alt1\">12</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number13 index12 alt2\">13</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number14 index13 alt1\">14</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number15 index14 alt2\">15</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number16 index15 alt1\">16</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number17 index16 alt2\">17</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number18 index17 alt1\">18</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number19 index18 alt2\">19</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number20 index19 alt1\">20</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number21 index20 alt2\">21</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number22 index21 alt1\">22</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number23 index22 alt2\">23</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number24 index23 alt1\">24</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number25 index24 alt2\">25</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number26 index25 alt1\">26</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number27 index26 alt2\">27</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number28 index27 alt1\">28</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td class=\"code\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\"><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">table</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">thead</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">tr</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number4 index3 alt1\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">th</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;Produto&lt;/</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">th</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number5 index4 alt2\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">th</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;Pre&ccedil;o&lt;/</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">th</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number6 index5 alt1\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">th</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;Quantidade&lt;/</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">th</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number7 index6 alt2\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;/</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">tr</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number8 index7 alt1\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;/</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">thead</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number9 index8 alt2\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">tbody</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number10 index9 alt1\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">tr</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number11 index10 alt2\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">td</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;Feij&atilde;o&lt;/</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">td</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number12 index11 alt1\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">td</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;R$ 8,75&lt;/</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">td</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number13 index12 alt2\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">td</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;1&lt;/</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">td</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number14 index13 alt1\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;/</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">tr</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number15 index14 alt2\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">tr</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number16 index15 alt1\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">td</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;Arroz&lt;/</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">td</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number17 index16 alt2\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">td</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;R$ 4,99&lt;/</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">td</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number18 index17 alt1\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">td</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;2&lt;/</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">td</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number19 index18 alt2\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;/</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">tr</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number20 index19 alt1\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;/</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">tbody</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number21 index20 alt2\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">tfoot</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number22 index21 alt1\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">tr</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number23 index22 alt2\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">td</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;Total&lt;/</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">td</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number24 index23 alt1\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">td</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;&lt;/</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">td</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number25 index24 alt2\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">td</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;R$ 18,73&lt;/</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">td</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number26 index25 alt1\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;/</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">tr</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number27 index26 alt2\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;/</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">tfoot</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number28 index27 alt1\"><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;/</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">table</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"code-caption\"><strong>Listagem 8</strong>. Tabela com cabe&ccedil;alho e rodap&eacute;</div>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><a class=\"btn-run\" title=\"Show me the code\" href=\"https://jsfiddle.net/2dyrLpL9/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Execute o c&oacute;digo</a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<figure class=\"lazy-img\"><img class=\"loaded\" src=\"https://arquivo.devmedia.com.br/artigos/Joel_Rodrigues/HTMLBasico/compactado/htmlbasico5.png\" alt=\"Tabela com cabe&ccedil;alho e rodap&eacute;\" />\r\n<figcaption><strong>Figura 5</strong>. Tabela com cabe&ccedil;alho e rodap&eacute;</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<div class=\"lf-nota\">Por padr&atilde;o, as tabelas n&atilde;o possuem bordas. Isso deve ser adicionado por meio das CSS.</div>\r\n<h3 id=\"listas\">Listas no HTML</h3>\r\n<p>Listas s&atilde;o elementos &uacute;teis para organizar e ordenar itens que est&atilde;o relacionados de alguma forma. No HTML &eacute; poss&iacute;vel criar tr&ecirc;s tipos de listas: ordenadas (com a tag&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">ol</span>), n&atilde;o ordenadas (com a tag&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">ul</span>), e de defini&ccedil;&atilde;o (por meio da tag&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">dl</span>).</p>\r\n<p>Na&nbsp;<strong>Listagem 9</strong>&nbsp;temos um exemplo de lista ordenada, enquanto a&nbsp;<strong>Listagem 10</strong>&nbsp;traz um exemplo de lista n&atilde;o ordenada. Em seguida, a&nbsp;<strong>Figura 6</strong>&nbsp;mostra o resultado dos dois c&oacute;digos. Observe que cada item das primeiras listas &eacute; definido pela tag&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">li</span>.</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-area\">\r\n<div class=\"pre_xml code-sample\">\r\n<div><code class=\"code-sample\"></code>\r\n<div>\r\n<div id=\"highlighter_738488\" class=\"syntaxhighlighter  xml\">\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"gutter\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\">1</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\">2</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\">3</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number4 index3 alt1\">4</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number5 index4 alt2\">5</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td class=\"code\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\"><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">ol</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">li</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;Item 1&lt;/</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">li</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">li</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;Item 2&lt;/</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">li</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number4 index3 alt1\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">li</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;Item 3&lt;/</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">li</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number5 index4 alt2\"><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;/</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">ol</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"code-caption\"><strong>Listagem 9</strong>. Lista ordenada</div>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><a class=\"btn-run\" title=\"Show me the code\" href=\"https://jsfiddle.net/vs41kusf/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Execute o c&oacute;digo</a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"code-area\">\r\n<div class=\"pre_xml code-sample\">\r\n<div><code class=\"code-sample\"></code>\r\n<div>\r\n<div id=\"highlighter_339429\" class=\"syntaxhighlighter  xml\">\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"gutter\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\">1</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\">2</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\">3</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number4 index3 alt1\">4</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number5 index4 alt2\">5</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td class=\"code\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\"><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">ul</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">li</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;Item 1&lt;/</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">li</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">li</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;Item 2&lt;/</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">li</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number4 index3 alt1\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">li</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;Item 3&lt;/</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">li</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number5 index4 alt2\"><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;/</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">ul</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"code-caption\"><strong>Listagem 10</strong>. Lista n&atilde;o ordenada</div>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><a class=\"btn-run\" title=\"Show me the code\" href=\"https://jsfiddle.net/oa4pftkh/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Execute o c&oacute;digo</a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<figure class=\"lazy-img\"><img class=\"loaded\" src=\"https://arquivo.devmedia.com.br/artigos/Joel_Rodrigues/HTMLBasico/compactado/htmlbasico6.png\" alt=\"Listas ordenada e n&atilde;o ordenada\" />\r\n<figcaption><strong>Figura 6</strong>. Listas ordenada e n&atilde;o ordenada</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<p>As listas de defini&ccedil;&atilde;o t&ecirc;m um comportamento um pouco diferente, uma vez que cada item &eacute; composto por um t&iacute;tulo (<span class=\"lf-badge\">dt</span>) e uma defini&ccedil;&atilde;o (<span class=\"lf-badge\">dd</span>), semelhante ao que ocorre em dicion&aacute;rios, nos quais temos os verbetes e suas defini&ccedil;&otilde;es. Na&nbsp;<strong>Listagem 11</strong>&nbsp;temos um exemplo desse tipo de lista, com seu resultado ilustrado na&nbsp;<strong>Figura 7</strong>.</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-area\">\r\n<div class=\"pre_xml code-sample\">\r\n<div><code class=\"code-sample\"></code>\r\n<div>\r\n<div id=\"highlighter_943128\" class=\"syntaxhighlighter  xml\">\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"gutter\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\">1</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\">2</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\">3</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number4 index3 alt1\">4</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number5 index4 alt2\">5</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number6 index5 alt1\">6</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number7 index6 alt2\">7</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number8 index7 alt1\">8</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td class=\"code\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\"><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">dl</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">dt</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;T&iacute;tulo 1&lt;/</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">dt</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">dd</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;Defini&ccedil;&atilde;o 1&lt;/</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">dd</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number4 index3 alt1\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">dt</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;T&iacute;tulo 2&lt;/</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">dt</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number5 index4 alt2\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">dd</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;Defini&ccedil;&atilde;o 2&lt;/</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">dd</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number6 index5 alt1\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">dt</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;T&iacute;tulo 3&lt;/</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">dt</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number7 index6 alt2\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">dd</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;Defini&ccedil;&atilde;o 3&lt;/</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">dd</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number8 index7 alt1\"><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;/</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">dl</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"code-caption\"><strong>Listagem 11</strong>. Exemplo de lista de defini&ccedil;&atilde;o</div>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><a class=\"btn-run\" title=\"Show me the code\" href=\"https://jsfiddle.net/Lv7vy6kk/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Execute o c&oacute;digo</a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3 id=\"formularios\">Formul&aacute;rios no HTML</h3>\r\n<p>Formul&aacute;rios s&atilde;o normalmente utilizados para integrar a p&aacute;gina HTML a algum processamento no lado servidor. Nesses casos, a p&aacute;gina envia dados para uma aplica&ccedil;&atilde;o (Java, PHP, .NET etc.), que os recebe, trata e retorna algum resultado.</p>\r\n<p>No HTML, geralmente usamos a tag&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">form</span>&nbsp;para delimitar a &aacute;rea na qual se encontram os campos a serem preenchidos pelo usu&aacute;rio, a fim de serem enviados para processamento no back-end (enquanto a p&aacute;gina HTML &eacute; chamada de front-end da aplica&ccedil;&atilde;o).</p>\r\n<p>A&nbsp;<strong>Listagem 12</strong>&nbsp;mostra um exemplo de formul&aacute;rio com v&aacute;rios tipos de campos para entrada de dados e um bot&atilde;o para submet&ecirc;-los ao servidor. Na&nbsp;<strong>Figura 8</strong>&nbsp;vemos seu resultado.</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-area\">\r\n<div class=\"pre_xml code-sample\">\r\n<div><code class=\"code-sample\"></code>\r\n<div>\r\n<div id=\"highlighter_914573\" class=\"syntaxhighlighter  xml\">\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"gutter\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\">1</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\">2</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\">3</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number4 index3 alt1\">4</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number5 index4 alt2\">5</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number6 index5 alt1\">6</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number7 index6 alt2\">7</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td class=\"code\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\"><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">form</code> <code class=\"xml color1\">action</code><code class=\"xml plain\">=</code><code class=\"xml string\">\"salvar_dados.php\"</code> <code class=\"xml color1\">method</code><code class=\"xml plain\">=</code><code class=\"xml string\">\"post\"</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">input</code> <code class=\"xml color1\">type</code><code class=\"xml plain\">=</code><code class=\"xml string\">\"text\"</code> <code class=\"xml color1\">placeholder</code><code class=\"xml plain\">=</code><code class=\"xml string\">\"Digite aqui\"</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt; &lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">br</code><code class=\"xml plain\">/&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">input</code> <code class=\"xml color1\">type</code><code class=\"xml plain\">=</code><code class=\"xml string\">\"checkbox\"</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;Checkbox &lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">br</code><code class=\"xml plain\">/&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number4 index3 alt1\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">input</code> <code class=\"xml color1\">type</code><code class=\"xml plain\">=</code><code class=\"xml string\">\"radio\"</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;Radio button &lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">br</code><code class=\"xml plain\">/&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number5 index4 alt2\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">input</code> <code class=\"xml color1\">type</code><code class=\"xml plain\">=</code><code class=\"xml string\">\"range\"</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt; &lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">br</code><code class=\"xml plain\">/&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number6 index5 alt1\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">input</code> <code class=\"xml color1\">type</code><code class=\"xml plain\">=</code><code class=\"xml string\">\"submit\"</code> <code class=\"xml color1\">value</code><code class=\"xml plain\">=</code><code class=\"xml string\">\"Enviar\"</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number7 index6 alt2\"><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;/</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">form</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"code-caption\"><strong>Listagem 12</strong>. Formul&aacute;rio com campos</div>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><a class=\"btn-run\" title=\"Show me the code\" href=\"https://jsfiddle.net/s9jtkoL4/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Execute o c&oacute;digo</a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<figure class=\"lazy-img\"><img class=\"loaded\" src=\"https://arquivo.devmedia.com.br/artigos/Joel_Rodrigues/HTMLBasico/compactado/htmlbasico8.png\" alt=\"HTML b&aacute;sico - c&oacute;digos HTML\" />\r\n<figcaption><strong>Figura 8</strong>. Formul&aacute;rio para envio de dados</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<h3 id=\"audio\">&Aacute;udio no HTML</h3>\r\n<p>Com HTML tamb&eacute;m &eacute; poss&iacute;vel inserir &aacute;udio e v&iacute;deo nas p&aacute;ginas com facilidade. Para &aacute;udio, podemos utilizar a tag&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">audio</span>, da mesma forma que apresentada na&nbsp;<strong>Listagem 14</strong>.</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-area\">\r\n<div class=\"pre_xml code-sample\">\r\n<div><code class=\"code-sample\"></code>\r\n<div>\r\n<div id=\"highlighter_674383\" class=\"syntaxhighlighter  xml\">\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"gutter\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\">1</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\">2</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\">3</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td class=\"code\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\"><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">audio</code> <code class=\"xml plain\">controls </code><code class=\"xml color1\">src</code><code class=\"xml plain\">=</code><code class=\"xml string\">\"musica.mp3\"</code> <code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml plain\">Seu browser n&atilde;o suporta &aacute;udio.</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\"><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;/</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">audio</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt; </code></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"code-caption\"><strong>Listagem 14</strong>. Inserindo &aacute;udio</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>Na tag audio, o atributo&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">src</span>&nbsp;aponta para o arquivo de &aacute;udio que ser&aacute; executado (MP3, OGG ou WAV). J&aacute; o atributo&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">controls</span>&nbsp;indica que devem ser exibidos os controles de gerenciamento do &aacute;udio (bot&otilde;es play, pause etc.). Al&eacute;m dele, outros tamb&eacute;m merecem destaque:&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">autoplay</span>, para fazer com que o &aacute;udio seja executado assim que for carregado;&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">loop</span>, para que o &aacute;udio seja executado repetidas vezes.</p>\r\n<div class=\"lf-nota\">Caso o browser n&atilde;o ofere&ccedil;a suporte a essa tag, o texto contido eu seu interior ser&aacute; exibido.</div>\r\n<p>Tamb&eacute;m podemos informar mais de um arquivo de &aacute;udio (op&ccedil;&otilde;es alternativas de formato, por exemplo). Nesse caso, precisamos utilizar a tag&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">source</span>, como no exemplo da&nbsp;<strong>Listagem 15</strong>.</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-area\">\r\n<div class=\"pre_xml code-sample\">\r\n<div><code class=\"code-sample\"></code>\r\n<div>\r\n<div id=\"highlighter_181690\" class=\"syntaxhighlighter  xml\">\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"gutter\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\">1</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\">2</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\">3</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number4 index3 alt1\">4</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td class=\"code\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\"><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">audio</code> <code class=\"xml plain\">controls </code><code class=\"xml color1\">src</code><code class=\"xml plain\">=</code><code class=\"xml string\">\"musica.mp3\"</code> <code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">source</code> <code class=\"xml color1\">src</code><code class=\"xml plain\">=</code><code class=\"xml string\">\"musica.ogg\"</code> <code class=\"xml color1\">type</code><code class=\"xml plain\">=</code><code class=\"xml string\">\"audio/ogg\"</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">source</code> <code class=\"xml color1\">src</code><code class=\"xml plain\">=</code><code class=\"xml string\">\"musica.mp3\"</code> <code class=\"xml color1\">type</code><code class=\"xml plain\">=</code><code class=\"xml string\">\"audio/mpeg\"</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number4 index3 alt1\"><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;/</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">audio</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"code-caption\"><strong>Listagem 15</strong>. Inserindo &aacute;udio com a tag source</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>Dessa vez, os arquivos ser&atilde;o buscados na ordem em que aparecem na lista. Caso um n&atilde;o seja localizado ou n&atilde;o possa ser carregado, o browser buscar&aacute; imediatamente o pr&oacute;ximo.</p>\r\n<p>A&nbsp;<strong>Figura 10</strong>&nbsp;ilustra o resultado desses c&oacute;digos, com o controle de &aacute;udio exibido no browser. Note tamb&eacute;m que no topo da janela (na aba do navegador) &eacute; exibido um &iacute;cone informando ao usu&aacute;rio que essa p&aacute;gina est&aacute; executando um &aacute;udio.</p>\r\n<figure class=\"lazy-img\"><img class=\"loaded\" src=\"https://arquivo.devmedia.com.br/artigos/Joel_Rodrigues/HTMLBasico/compactado/htmlbasico10.png\" alt=\"HTML b&aacute;sico - c&oacute;digos HTML\" /><br />\r\n<figcaption><strong>Figura 10</strong>. &Aacute;udio em execu&ccedil;&atilde;o na p&aacute;gina</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>Saiba mais sobre&nbsp;<a title=\"video em HTML5\" href=\"https://www.devmedia.com.br/html-video-como-adicionar-e-reproduzir-videos-em-html-utilizando-dom/28790\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">como adicionar &aacute;udio e v&iacute;deo com HTML5</a></p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<h3 id=\"video\">V&iacute;deo no HTML</h3>\r\n<p>Semelhante ao &aacute;udio, tamb&eacute;m podemos inserir v&iacute;deos nas p&aacute;ginas HTML utilizando a tag&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">video</span>, adicionada na HTML5, como na&nbsp;<strong>Listagem 16</strong>.</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-area\">\r\n<div class=\"pre_xml code-sample\">\r\n<div><code class=\"code-sample\"></code>\r\n<div>\r\n<div id=\"highlighter_139377\" class=\"syntaxhighlighter  xml\">\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"gutter\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\">1</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\">2</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\">3</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td class=\"code\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\"><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">video</code> <code class=\"xml color1\">src</code><code class=\"xml plain\">=</code><code class=\"xml string\">\"video.mp4\"</code> <code class=\"xml color1\">width</code><code class=\"xml plain\">=</code><code class=\"xml string\">\"640\"</code> <code class=\"xml color1\">height</code><code class=\"xml plain\">=</code><code class=\"xml string\">\"480\"</code> <code class=\"xml plain\">controls&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml plain\">Seu browser n&atilde;o suporta v&iacute;deo HTML5.</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\"><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;/</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">video</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"code-caption\"><strong>Listagem 16</strong>. Inserindo v&iacute;deo</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>Dessa vez, al&eacute;m dos atributos j&aacute; vistos no &aacute;udio, tamb&eacute;m precisamos informar a largura (<span class=\"lf-badge\">width</span>) e a altura (<span class=\"lf-badge\">height</span>) do v&iacute;deo, a fim de mant&ecirc;-lo adequado ao layout.</p>\r\n<p>O c&oacute;digo da&nbsp;<strong>Listagem 17</strong>&nbsp;pode ser utilizado quando desejarmos informar mais de um arquivo de v&iacute;deo como op&ccedil;&otilde;es de carregamento, da mesma forma que vimos na tag&nbsp;<span class=\"lf-badge\">audio</span>. Nesse caso, os formatos suportados s&atilde;o MP4, WebM e Ogg.</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-area\">\r\n<div class=\"pre_xml code-sample\">\r\n<div><code class=\"code-sample\"></code>\r\n<div>\r\n<div id=\"highlighter_870960\" class=\"syntaxhighlighter  xml\">\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"gutter\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\">1</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\">2</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\">3</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number4 index3 alt1\">4</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td class=\"code\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\"><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">video</code> <code class=\"xml color1\">width</code><code class=\"xml plain\">=</code><code class=\"xml string\">\"640\"</code> <code class=\"xml color1\">height</code><code class=\"xml plain\">=</code><code class=\"xml string\">\"480\"</code> <code class=\"xml plain\">controls&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">source</code> <code class=\"xml color1\">src</code><code class=\"xml plain\">=</code><code class=\"xml string\">\"video.webm\"</code> <code class=\"xml color1\">type</code><code class=\"xml plain\">=</code><code class=\"xml string\">\"video/webm\"</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\"><code class=\"xml spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">source</code> <code class=\"xml color1\">src</code><code class=\"xml plain\">=</code><code class=\"xml string\">\"video.mp4\"</code> <code class=\"xml color1\">type</code><code class=\"xml plain\">=</code><code class=\"xml string\">\"video/mp4\"</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number4 index3 alt1\"><code class=\"xml plain\">&lt;/</code><code class=\"xml keyword\">video</code><code class=\"xml plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"code-caption\"><strong>Listagem 17</strong>. Inserindo v&iacute;deo</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>O resultado agora pode ser visto na&nbsp;<strong>Figura 11</strong>.</p>\r\n<figure class=\"lazy-img\"><img class=\"loaded\" src=\"https://arquivo.devmedia.com.br/artigos/Joel_Rodrigues/HTMLBasico/compactado/htmlbasico11.png\" alt=\"V&iacute;deo em execu&ccedil;&atilde;o na p&aacute;gina\" />\r\n<figcaption><strong>Figura 11</strong>. V&iacute;deo em execu&ccedil;&atilde;o na p&aacute;gina</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<hr />','2020-02-25 14:44:26','2020-02-25 14:44:26',8),(9,'Flutter: porque você deveria apostar nesta tecnologia','Flutter:-porque-voce-deveria-apostar-nesta-tecnologia','<p>Primeiro come&ccedil;arei contando o motivo de ter escolhido aprender e especializar em desenvolvimento h&iacute;brido com Flutter inv&eacute;s de virar especialista React Native e o motivo &eacute; bem simples:&nbsp;<strong>Fluidez</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id=\"react-native\">React Native</h2>\r\n<p>Para quem j&aacute; desenvolveu aplicativos nativos sabe a dificuldade de manter o c&oacute;digo atualizado caso o aplicativo tiver obrigatoriedade de funcionar nas duas plataformas&nbsp;<em>Android</em>&nbsp;e&nbsp;<em>iOS</em>. Enxergando essa defici&ecirc;ncia a equipe do&nbsp;<em>Facebook</em>&nbsp;criou o&nbsp;<strong>React Native</strong>&nbsp;e disponibilizou-o como framework open source no ano de 2015 para o p&uacute;blico.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 id=\"o-que-&eacute;-esse-tal-de-react-native\">O que &eacute; esse tal de React Native?</h3>\r\n<p>React Native &eacute; um framework de desenvolvimento h&iacute;brido utilizando Javascript como base para criar aplicativos nativos utilizando apenas um c&oacute;digo fonte padr&atilde;o. Diferente do&nbsp;<strong>ionic</strong>&nbsp;que tamb&eacute;m servia para criar aplicativos h&iacute;bridos, o React Native n&atilde;o funciona sobre uma WebView, ele possui uma&nbsp;<em>engine</em>&nbsp;(bridge) que ao emular o aplicativo no aparelho essa bridge faz um mapeamento dos componentes criados usando javascript com os componentes nativos do SO, aumentando assim o desempenho do aplicativo.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 id=\"problemas-ao-utilizar-react-native\">Problemas ao utilizar React Native</h3>\r\n<p>Embora React Native seja uma das melhores solu&ccedil;&otilde;es para construir aplicativos h&iacute;bridos, ele ainda n&atilde;o possui a mesma fluidez de um aplicativo constru&iacute;do utilizando apenas recursos nativo, e mesmo que ainda haja muitas empresas utilizando-o em seus aplicativos a sociedade n&atilde;o &eacute; mais a mesma do ano de lan&ccedil;amento (2015), as pessoas est&atilde;o cada vez mais impacientes e qualquer gargalo durante o uso &eacute; motivo para desinstalar o aplicativo.</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://cdn-images-1.medium.com/max/800/1*k_aQA6TG9rrqu8gz0drG9g.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"733\" height=\"253\" /><span class=\"figcaption_hack\">Analisando os gr&aacute;ficos acima referentes a pesquisas realizadas durante o ano de&nbsp;<sup>2018</sup>&frasl;<sub>2019</sub>&nbsp;percebe-se a crescente busca por flutter</span></p>\r\n<h3 id=\"flutter-uma-nova-solu&ccedil;&atilde;o\">Flutter: uma nova solu&ccedil;&atilde;o</h3>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://cdn-images-1.medium.com/max/600/1*42zsz13tv08yERlHsZCdOw.gif\" alt=\"\" /><span class=\"figcaption_hack\">Demonstra&ccedil;&atilde;o aplicativo em&nbsp;<a href=\"https://flutter.dev/\">Flutter</a></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Com a mesma proposta do React Native de criar aplicativos h&iacute;bridos utilizando apenas uma base de c&oacute;digo surgiu o Flutter, desenvolvido e atualizado pela equipe da Google.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id=\"o-que-&eacute;-flutter\">O que &eacute; Flutter?</h2>\r\n<p>Como dito anteriormente, o Flutter &eacute; um framework para desenvolvimento h&iacute;brido de aplicativos utilizando a linguagem&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.dartlang.org/\">Dart</a>&nbsp;como base de cria&ccedil;&atilde;o dos aplicativos.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id=\"porque-usar-flutter\">Porque usar Flutter?</h2>\r\n<p>Diferente do React Native que possui um intermedi&aacute;rio (bridge) entre a UI e o dispositivo, o Flutter fica na camada do UI e n&atilde;o chama os componentes nativos do SO, ele &eacute;&nbsp;<strong>desenhado diretamente</strong>&nbsp;em um canvas que aumenta a performance e fluidez a n&iacute;vel de um aplicativo desenvolvido exclusivamente nativo. Al&eacute;m do ganho com performance o Flutter &eacute; uma tecnologia recente de f&aacute;cil aprendizado e j&aacute; possui algumas features sendo desenvolvidas, dentre elas:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Flutter para Web</li>\r\n<li>Flutter para Desktop</li>\r\n<li>&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Ou seja, voc&ecirc; ir&aacute; construir um aplicativo que poder&aacute; ser reaproveitado para suas web applications e tamb&eacute;m desktop. Esse &eacute; um sonho para muitos desenvolvedores, ter apenas uma base de c&oacute;digo para toda a camada de apresenta&ccedil;&atilde;o.</p>\r\n<p>Al&eacute;m dos benef&iacute;cios de performance nativa, o Flutter possui muita flexibilidade para a cria&ccedil;&atilde;o de UI personalizadas, anima&ccedil;&otilde;es e facilidade em acessar os recursos do aparelho (geolocaliza&ccedil;&atilde;o, galeria, etc&hellip;).</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id=\"como-funciona-o-flutter\">Como funciona o flutter?</h2>\r\n<p>Se voc&ecirc; est&aacute; habituado com o termo &ldquo;componente&rdquo; vai se identificar r&aacute;pido. O Flutter possui os &ldquo;widgets&rdquo; que seria a mesma coisa de um componente. Um widget &eacute; uma &aacute;rvore que pode conter um ou mais filhos(widgets), e esses filhos s&atilde;o renderizados conforme a constru&ccedil;&atilde;o desta &aacute;rvore. Muito parecido com o DOM do html.</p>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://cdn-images-1.medium.com/max/800/1*j49HIY0az28VWMDrmUu9eg.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"609\" height=\"431\" /></p>\r\n<p>Abaixo um exemplo de widget na pr&aacute;tica</p>\r\n<div id=\"gist95576224\" class=\"gist\">\r\n<div class=\"gist-file\">\r\n<div class=\"gist-data\">\r\n<div class=\"js-gist-file-update-container js-task-list-container file-box\">\r\n<div id=\"file-widget-dart\" class=\"file\">\r\n<div class=\"Box-body p-0 blob-wrapper data type-dart \">\r\n<table class=\"highlight tab-size js-file-line-container\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" data-tab-size=\"8\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td id=\"file-widget-dart-L1\" class=\"blob-num js-line-number\" data-line-number=\"1\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td id=\"file-widget-dart-LC1\" class=\"blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line\"><span class=\"pl-c1\">Widget</span> <span class=\"pl-en\">build</span>(<span class=\"pl-c1\">BuildContext</span> context) {</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td id=\"file-widget-dart-L2\" class=\"blob-num js-line-number\" data-line-number=\"2\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td id=\"file-widget-dart-LC2\" class=\"blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line\"><span class=\"pl-k\">return</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">Container</span>(</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td id=\"file-widget-dart-L3\" class=\"blob-num js-line-number\" data-line-number=\"3\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td id=\"file-widget-dart-LC3\" class=\"blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line\">color<span class=\"pl-k\">:</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">Colors</span>.amber,</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td id=\"file-widget-dart-L4\" class=\"blob-num js-line-number\" data-line-number=\"4\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td id=\"file-widget-dart-LC4\" class=\"blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line\">child<span class=\"pl-k\">:</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">Center</span>(</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td id=\"file-widget-dart-L5\" class=\"blob-num js-line-number\" data-line-number=\"5\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td id=\"file-widget-dart-LC5\" class=\"blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line\">child<span class=\"pl-k\">:</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">Text</span>(<span class=\"pl-s\">\'Exemplo de widget com flutter\'</span>, style<span class=\"pl-k\">:</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">TextStyle</span>(color<span class=\"pl-k\">:</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">Colors</span>.black))</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td id=\"file-widget-dart-L6\" class=\"blob-num js-line-number\" data-line-number=\"6\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td id=\"file-widget-dart-LC6\" class=\"blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line\">),</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td id=\"file-widget-dart-L7\" class=\"blob-num js-line-number\" data-line-number=\"7\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td id=\"file-widget-dart-LC7\" class=\"blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line\">);</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td id=\"file-widget-dart-L8\" class=\"blob-num js-line-number\" data-line-number=\"8\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td id=\"file-widget-dart-LC8\" class=\"blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line\">}</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"gist-meta\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://gist.github.com/fabianosanttana/dade0549cbcbfaf1b5ce0351f9f5cb4d/raw/a6b109ead8b432f89d56c31c09af43947767df99/widget.dart\">view raw</a><a href=\"https://gist.github.com/fabianosanttana/dade0549cbcbfaf1b5ce0351f9f5cb4d#file-widget-dart\">widget.dart</a>&nbsp;hosted with ❤ by&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/\">GitHub</a></div>\r\n<div class=\"gist-meta\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>Observe acima, temos&nbsp;<strong>Container</strong>&nbsp;que possui uma propriedade&nbsp;<strong>child</strong>&nbsp;que pode receber outro widget, no exemplo utilizei&nbsp;<strong>Center</strong>&nbsp;que por sua vez possui suas propriedades e tamb&eacute;m tem uma propriedade **child&nbsp;<strong>que pode receber outro widget</strong>.**</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id=\"fuchsia-o-novo-os-do-google\">Fuchsia: O novo OS do google</h2>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://cdn-images-1.medium.com/max/800/1*2af3pcH8Ue-uTLkJoEElAw.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"487\" height=\"221\" /></p>\r\n<p>Se voc&ecirc; &eacute; um profissional que quer estar na frente, vai uma dica para voc&ecirc;. O Google est&aacute; lan&ccedil;ando um novo sistema para mobile, ainda n&atilde;o se sabe se esse sistema substituir&aacute; Android, se o React Native dar&aacute; suporte por&eacute;m o que se sabe &eacute; que&nbsp;<strong>Flutter</strong>&nbsp;ser&aacute; usado para criar aplicativos para esse novo sistema.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id=\"conclus&atilde;o\">Conclus&atilde;o</h2>\r\n<p>Mesmo sendo uma tecnologia recente e sem mercado, aprender Flutter &eacute; uma aposta que pode dar muito certo. Algumas grandes empresas (Alibaba, Groupon, Google, etc&hellip;) notaram isso e est&atilde;o migrando para Flutter.</p>\r\n<p>Quando comecei a aprender eu achei realmente muito divertido a constru&ccedil;&atilde;o de aplicativos usando Dart. Outra coisa, conhecimento nunca &eacute; demais, se voc&ecirc; j&aacute; desenvolve em React Native como eu, aprender mais uma tecnologia n&atilde;o ir&aacute; te diminuir como profissional.</p>','2020-02-25 14:50:03','2020-02-25 14:50:03',10);
